              </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129711\" data-seq=\"1898129809\" data-pid=\"1898129711\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"6184435\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129711.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d7/b2/d5d2b108d8a9c38abba80f0691c2bb51.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d7/b2/d5d2b108d8a9c38abba80f0691c2bb51.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d7/b2/d5d2b108d8a9c38abba80f0691c2bb51.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129711\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/6184435.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6184435\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州烟台山公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129712\" data-seq=\"1898129810\" data-pid=\"1898129712\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"6184435\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129712.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/89/90/3899d204fd19a71022d75024dd7e6559.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/89/90/3899d204fd19a71022d75024dd7e6559.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/89/90/3899d204fd19a71022d75024dd7e6559.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129712\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/6184435.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6184435\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州烟台山公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898130290\" data-seq=\"1898130339\" data-pid=\"1898130290\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"6184435\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898130290.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/40/14/a4f0d5de55b5a8c46564df893709b408.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/40/14/a4f0d5de55b5a8c46564df893709b408.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/40/14/a4f0d5de55b5a8c46564df893709b408.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898130290\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/6184435.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6184435\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州烟台山公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898997910\">\r\n                                                                                                        1856年的哥特式“石厝教堂”，是\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11498.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"福州\" target=\"_blank\">福州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            现存最古老的教堂建筑。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129713\" data-seq=\"1898129811\" data-pid=\"1898129713\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"6184435\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129713.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/24/9e/40619489c2e6905b556caf9396cae87e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/24/9e/40619489c2e6905b556caf9396cae87e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/24/9e/40619489c2e6905b556caf9396cae87e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129713\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/6184435.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6184435\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州烟台山公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129714\" data-seq=\"1898129812\" data-pid=\"1898129714\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"6184435\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129714.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3b/44/d661045b31630b3d0c7f6cdb88dc0fe9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3b/44/d661045b31630b3d0c7f6cdb88dc0fe9.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3b/44/d661045b31630b3d0c7f6cdb88dc0fe9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129714\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/6184435.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6184435\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州烟台山公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129715\" data-seq=\"1898129813\" data-pid=\"1898129715\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"6184435\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129715.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/36/f8/7e0af3b7fc8e09713a724aab3a049068.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/36/f8/7e0af3b7fc8e09713a724aab3a049068.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/36/f8/7e0af3b7fc8e09713a724aab3a049068.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129715\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/6184435.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6184435\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州烟台山公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129716\" data-seq=\"1898129814\" data-pid=\"1898129716\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"6184435\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129716.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/76/53/fa4f5eba340b701944a1d81f2aef527f.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/76/53/fa4f5eba340b701944a1d81f2aef527f.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/76/53/fa4f5eba340b701944a1d81f2aef527f.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129716\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/6184435.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6184435\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州烟台山公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898996779\">\r\n                                                                                                        离开喧闹的主街，拐入安静的居民区时，似乎才是\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11243.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"烟台\" target=\"_blank\">烟台</a>\r\n                                                                                                            山真正的面目。各种旧址的路标，黑夜中的教堂，铺满墙的盛放的三角梅，灯光变换的“水母”路，钢琴图案的路标和猫咪图案的门牌...是新与旧的和谐交融。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129717\" data-seq=\"1898129815\" data-pid=\"1898129717\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"6184435\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129717.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/09/06/482f159b6ea9017003a4685ac9e1db33.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/09/06/482f159b6ea9017003a4685ac9e1db33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/09/06/482f159b6ea9017003a4685ac9e1db33.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129717\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/6184435.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"6184435\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州烟台山公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898997117\">\r\n                                                                                                        大家都说\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11243.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"烟台\" target=\"_blank\">烟台</a>\r\n                                                                                                            山的夜晚更热闹更值得游玩，但如果想走走小巷，看看各处旧处痕迹，还是天亮时来更合适。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898997168\" data-index=\"13\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">-爱情岛</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898997223\">\r\n                                                                                                        门票：无门票 游玩时间：0.5-1h<br>\r\n从\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11243.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"烟台\" target=\"_blank\">烟台</a>\r\n                                                                                                            山沿着闽江慢慢走，便来到了爱情岛。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129718\" data-seq=\"1898129816\" data-pid=\"1898129718\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129718.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 947px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/09/ef/ef7f83741ac9b2c3db072f02149b6c76.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/09/ef/ef7f83741ac9b2c3db072f02149b6c76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/09/ef/ef7f83741ac9b2c3db072f02149b6c76.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129718\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129719\" data-seq=\"1898129817\" data-pid=\"1898129719\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129719.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c0/28/f004e63768c0ea846a77d2e2b6b302dd.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c0/28/f004e63768c0ea846a77d2e2b6b302dd.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c0/28/f004e63768c0ea846a77d2e2b6b302dd.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129719\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129720\" data-seq=\"1898129818\" data-pid=\"1898129720\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129720.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/4a/01e7166c307a0c82999062019430b794.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/4a/01e7166c307a0c82999062019430b794.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/4a/01e7166c307a0c82999062019430b794.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129720\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898997555\">\r\n                                                                                                        彩色的爱情岛和黑白色的三县洲大桥在夜幕下成了鲜明对比。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129721\" data-seq=\"1898129819\" data-pid=\"1898129721\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129721.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8b/bf/d87c5dc0254620331b5f195f22e695a0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8b/bf/d87c5dc0254620331b5f195f22e695a0.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8b/bf/d87c5dc0254620331b5f195f22e695a0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129721\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129722\" data-seq=\"1898129820\" data-pid=\"1898129722\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129722.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3a/36/d4ebf46f3dc7a850e6bd2838bd811118.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3a/36/d4ebf46f3dc7a850e6bd2838bd811118.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3a/36/d4ebf46f3dc7a850e6bd2838bd811118.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129722\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898997571\">\r\n                                                                                                        爱情岛上到处是人工痕迹。爱心垃圾桶，挂满红条的祈愿树，江边的爱心座椅，散布在椅背和路上的情话，处处都是打卡点，适合拍照但趣味性不足。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898130291\" data-seq=\"1898130340\" data-pid=\"1898130291\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898130291.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/50/84/f425d04366ee262fe66886cab2a8f789.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/50/84/f425d04366ee262fe66886cab2a8f789.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/50/84/f425d04366ee262fe66886cab2a8f789.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898130291\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129723\" data-seq=\"1898129821\" data-pid=\"1898129723\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129723.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/17/62/566e6bc69bed59059b3e4c6c5ca5be40.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/17/62/566e6bc69bed59059b3e4c6c5ca5be40.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/17/62/566e6bc69bed59059b3e4c6c5ca5be40.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129723\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898997642\">\r\n                                                                                                        我们在岛边找了处座位，这一天的行程在微微江风，点点灯火中结束，也很符合\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11498.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"福州\" target=\"_blank\">福州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的惬意。<br>\r\n建议白天来，夜晚很多灯都关了，大多景观看不到。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898997782\" data-index=\"14\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">-基督教花巷堂</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898997819\">\r\n                                                                                                        门票：无门票 游玩时间：15min<br>\r\n在叶家花生汤吃饭时看到对街涌出了巨大人流，大多是些本地的阿嬷和爷叔们。好奇走近一看，竟是个超美貌的粉色教堂。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129732\" data-seq=\"1898129830\" data-pid=\"1898129732\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"56046676\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129732.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/fd/4f/95b2ba89e354f049b3080ec12886fc59.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/fd/4f/95b2ba89e354f049b3080ec12886fc59.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/fd/4f/95b2ba89e354f049b3080ec12886fc59.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129732\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/56046676.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"56046676\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>基督教花巷堂\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129733\" data-seq=\"1898129831\" data-pid=\"1898129733\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"56046676\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129733.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2f/fd/eb3beef960caf903a6a9406016bd6554.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2f/fd/eb3beef960caf903a6a9406016bd6554.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2f/fd/eb3beef960caf903a6a9406016bd6554.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129733\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/56046676.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"56046676\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>基督教花巷堂\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898998536\">\r\n                                                                                                        不同于我之前见过的一些好看教堂偏景点性质，花巷堂更具生活气息。游客很少，大多还是来教堂里做礼拜，合在树下避荫的信徒，门外长桌旁的年轻人很积极地传教，歌声绕过彩色玻璃窗，充盈着整片教堂区域。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129734\" data-seq=\"1898129832\" data-pid=\"1898129734\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"56046676\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129734.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e8/e4/40aa6b82b37c60eee116a0fc4ada59e1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e8/e4/40aa6b82b37c60eee116a0fc4ada59e1.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e8/e4/40aa6b82b37c60eee116a0fc4ada59e1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129734\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/56046676.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"56046676\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>基督教花巷堂\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129735\" data-seq=\"1898129833\" data-pid=\"1898129735\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"56046676\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129735.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f5/b0/cc3e20d5edf2100f5885d3ee97a412e1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f5/b0/cc3e20d5edf2100f5885d3ee97a412e1.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%