nfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>基督教花巷堂\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898998770\" data-index=\"15\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">-三坊七巷</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898998947\">\r\n                                                                                                        门票：无门票 游览时间：3-4h<br>\r\n“西三坊，东七巷”，三坊七巷的历史悠久，发轫于晋，形成于唐，鼎盛于明清。街区坊巷相连，乌墙黛瓦，被誉为“里坊制度活化石”。<br>\r\n三坊七巷曾住过的名人多达四百多位，如今仍保留着冰心故居，林则徐纪念馆，严复故居等。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129724\" data-seq=\"1898129822\" data-pid=\"1898129724\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"15419\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129724.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7a/b3/6645ab2782fffaf202b30084053e3acf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7a/b3/6645ab2782fffaf202b30084053e3acf.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7a/b3/6645ab2782fffaf202b30084053e3acf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129724\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/15419.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15419\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>三坊七巷\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n       