      "title": "A concert-inspired Nanyang Rhapsody: Lion City Flash Mob • Malaysia Slow Shake",
      "descr": "It all started with a concert\r\nIn June 2023, Taylor Swift officially announced her Asia concert schedule.\r\nUnfortunately, there are only two Asian races, Japan and Singapore.\r\nAs a loyal fan who has followed her for more than a decade, hope was ignited in my heart and I decided to grab a ticket no matter what.\r\nI tried to grab tickets for both Japan and Singapore, and after a lot of ups and downs, I was lucky enough to get tickets for the concert in Singapore on March 3rd.",
      "cover": "http://localhost:9090/files/download/55.jpeg",
      "content": "<div class=\"vc_article\">\r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            <div class=\"va_con _j_master_content\" data-cs-t=\"ginfo_kw_hotel\">\r\n    <div class=\"block-loading loading_backward\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"_j_content_box\">\r\n\t        <div data-seq=\"1898439278\" data-index=\"1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">一切源于一场演唱会</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898439296\">\r\n                                                                                                        2023年6月，泰勒·斯威夫特官宣了她的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/52314.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"亚洲\" target=\"_blank\">亚洲</a>\r\n                                                                                                            演唱会行程。<br>\r\n可惜的是，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/52314.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"亚洲\" target=\"_blank\">亚洲</a>\r\n                                                                                                            场次仅有\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10183.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"日本\" target=\"_blank\">日本</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            两站。<br>\r\n作为一名追随了她十多年的忠实粉丝，我心中燃起了希望，决定无论如何都要抢到一张票。<br>\r\n我尝试同时抢\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10183.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"日本\" target=\"_blank\">日本</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的门票，这期间历经波折与失望，还好最终幸运地获得了\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            3月3日演唱会的门票。<br>\r\n有了这张珍贵的门票，我开始马不停蹄地规划行程。<br>\r\n今年各个国家的政策也相当友好，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10097.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"马来西亚\" target=\"_blank\">马来西亚</a>\r\n                                                                                                            先后对\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            实行免签政策，这让我可以无拘无束地在这两个国家之间穿梭游玩。于是，我决定把\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10097.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"马来西亚\" target=\"_blank\">马来西亚</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的旅行结合起来，开启一段丰富多彩的双城之旅。<br>\r\n为了这碟醋包了一顿饺子，不过也有很多预料之外的快乐：\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898457592\">\r\n                                                                                                        \uD83D\uDC97被伊斯兰的艺术魅力深深吸引了;\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898457922\" data-seq=\"1898457923\" data-pid=\"1898457922\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"5578271\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898457922.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ce/7d/baeadeeec490d9d73c2419c5bced7eee.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ce/7d/baeadeeec490d9d73c2419c5bced7eee.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ce/7d/baeadeeec490d9d73c2419c5bced7eee.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898457922\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/5578271.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5578271\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>马来西亚伊斯兰艺术博物馆\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898327663\" data-seq=\"1898327763\" data-pid=\"1898327663\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"5578271\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898327663.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/65/46972b87110c077b6e95b384b8791630.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/65/46972b87110c077b6e95b384b8791630.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/13/65/46972b87110c077b6e95b384b8791630.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898327663\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/5578271.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5578271\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>马来西亚伊斯兰艺术博物馆\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898456759\">\r\n                                                                                                        \uD83D\uDC97在喜欢的热带雨林中漫游，偶遇各种小动物；\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898440485\" data-seq=\"1898440486\" data-pid=\"1898440485\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898440485.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/e3/0e02f8d0445d475854a2e247cc35f4f4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/e3/0e02f8d0445d475854a2e247cc35f4f4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/e3/0e02f8d0445d475854a2e247cc35f4f4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898440485\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898457201\" data-seq=\"1898457202\" data-pid=\"1898457201\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"5432079\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898457201.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/05/b3/79cda35e4aa03afac863f4f90d4667db.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/05/b3/79cda35e4aa03afac863f4f90d4667db.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/05/b3/79cda35e4aa03afac863f4f90d4667db.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898457201\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/5432079.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5432079\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>槟城升旗山\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898444339\" data-seq=\"1898444340\" data-pid=\"1898444339\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898444339.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/fb/48cef6f18c3088148878b1ded42f19c1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/fb/48cef6f18c3088148878b1ded42f19c1.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/fb/48cef6f18c3088148878b1ded42f19c1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898444339\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898457244\">\r\n                                                                                                        \uD83D\uDC97不会游泳的我体验了被热带鱼群包围的快乐；\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898457259\" data-seq=\"1898457260\" data-pid=\"1898457259\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"76089784\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898457259.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 379px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/00/8cd665f3a3a4a2707c826cf1e3c2bf31.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/00/8cd665f3a3a4a2707c826cf1e3c2bf31.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/00/8cd665f3a3a4a2707c826cf1e3c2bf31.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898457259\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/76089784.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"76089784\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>马努干岛海底漫步\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"video_wrapper _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898460066\">\r\n            <div class=\"add_video _j_seqitem \" data-vid=\"3567201\" data-seq=\"1898460066\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3567201?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D&amp;type=.m3u8\" data-type=\"2\" data-ready=\"1\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"800\" data-audit=\"0\"><video data-type=\"2\" width=\"680\" height=\"auto\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3567201?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D\" class=\"_js_videojs_hls\" data-noneedinit=\"0\" controls=\"\" src=\"blob:https://www.mafengwo.cn/f737fdbc-8da8-4f8a-aeac-c305a05faf21\"></video></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        \r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898445183\" data-seq=\"1898445184\" data-pid=\"1898445183\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898445183.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e4/c3/e4cc32af45df720507fd59d2e4000779.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e4/c3/e4cc32af45df720507fd59d2e4000779.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e4/c3/e4cc32af45df720507fd59d2e4000779.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898445183\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898457963\">\r\n                                                                                                        \uD83D\uDC97日落，永远是大自然最动人的景色。无论它轮回多少次，就是无法厌倦；\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898458671\" data-seq=\"1898458672\" data-pid=\"1898458671\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"5485715\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898458671.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/7c/1470c7d9280cc720538abd9dbebabadb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/7c/1470c7d9280cc720538abd9dbebabadb.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/7c/1470c7d9280cc720538abd9dbebabadb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898458671\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/5485715.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5485715\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>丹绒亚路海滩\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898444400\" data-seq=\"1898444401\" data-pid=\"1898444400\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898444400.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/dc/18c82eeeb0988ce6609db66b8df2cadf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/dc/18c82eeeb0988ce6609db66b8df2cadf.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/dc/18c82eeeb0988ce6609db66b8df2cadf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898444400\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898444508\" data-seq=\"1898444509\" data-pid=\"1898444508\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898444508.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 509px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/7f/9f46e73e982bf8c6f38da6f6642aca05.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/7f/9f46e73e982bf8c6f38da6f6642aca05.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/7f/9f46e73e982bf8c6f38da6f6642aca05.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898444508\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898440373\" data-seq=\"1898440374\" data-pid=\"1898440373\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898440373.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/7f/61b77259cc83f9ddb64235098a8b2c92.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/7f/61b77259cc83f9ddb64235098a8b2c92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/da/7f/61b77259cc83f9ddb64235098a8b2c92.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898440373\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898458126\" data-index=\"2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">行程概览</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898458131\">\r\n                                                                                                        因为Taylor Swift演唱会那几天\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的酒店价格很高，所以尽量缩减了在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的时间。<br>\r\n个人认为\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10097.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"马来西亚\" target=\"_blank\">马来西亚</a>\r\n                                                                                                            非常适合第一次出国的朋友们，如果你跟我一样喜欢自然和艺术，完全可以一比一复制我的行程。当然\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的行程还是有点\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144799.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"太特\" target=\"_blank\">太特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            种兵了，分成两天玩会舒适很多。<br>\r\n✨每个景点后面我都会标注参观攻略，以及每个国家后面都有关于我踩过的坑的一些注意事项，大家可以在目录上随意跳转只取所需~\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898458472\" data-seq=\"1898458473\" data-pid=\"1898458472\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898458472.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 752px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/1f/650c626e2097f2472a6e1e41e547a50e.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/1f/650c626e2097f2472a6e1e41e547a50e.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/1f/650c626e2097f2472a6e1e41e547a50e.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898458472\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898458538\" data-index=\"3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">---------新加坡篇---------</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898458555\" data-index=\"4\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">初见</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898458572\">\r\n                                                                                                        第一次尝试一个人出国。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，对于从小就生活在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16107.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"大城\" target=\"_blank\">大城</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市的我来说，并没有太大的诱惑力。<br>\r\n旁人一提起\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，我的脑海里就会出现这样的画面：在一个会喷水的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145844.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"狮子\" target=\"_blank\">狮子</a>\r\n                                                                                                            雕塑旁，周围是高楼大厦，那是钢筋水泥组成的怪兽，无处不在地向游客展示高科技以及井井有条的生活方式。即使是公园，也是人工打造的精品，看那些勉强在铁丝巨网中生长的植物，对，我指的是它的地标性景点空中花园。还有过高的吃住成本，在理性驱动下实在没有太多放开去玩的冲动。<br>\r\n也许就是被这些先入为主的观念束缚着，我迟迟没定下行程路线，或许我应该随心所欲一点，看能否在其中碰撞出有趣火花。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898516969\" data-seq=\"1898516970\" data-pid=\"1898516969\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898516969.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/e6/92bb74da3a92764b13136d10d2e3baf8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/e6/92bb74da3a92764b13136d10d2e3baf8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/e6/92bb74da3a92764b13136d10d2e3baf8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898516969\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898516971\">\r\n                                                                                                        凌晨4点多到达\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            樟宜机场，我想说\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            会惩罚每一个不认真做攻略的人。<br>\r\n我原本想着到\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            后先美滋滋地找个位置躺一觉，醒来之后逛逛\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64188.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"大名\" target=\"_blank\">大名</a>\r\n                                                                                                            鼎鼎的机场瀑布（那时候并不知道机场瀑布不是24小时开放的），差不多再去酒店办理入住。<br>\r\n然而我一下飞机，急速通过机器过关，去拿行李，打算找分布在机场各处的舒服躺椅，结果发现我兜兜转转了好久都找不到，再往前走一点点商铺又关门了一片漆黑。此时我已经拿行李出了到达大厅，并不能再回去找付费休息室，只好放弃折腾，随便找了个位置坐着休息。<br>\r\n既然机场逛不了，那我问一下能不能提前入住吧。结果发现自己没开国际漫游，又折腾了好久，最后操着一口不怎么流利的英语（谁懂应试教育下哑巴英语的痛）问到了如果想提前入住要加钱升级房型。<br>\r\n与其在机场浪费时间，那不如直接去酒店放下行李直接去逛吧。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n原本以为今天自己的遭遇已经够Drama了，不过，更Drama的永远在下一刻。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n看着在Grab上面叫的出租车在机场外绕了10几分钟，积压的怨气让我变得渐渐不耐烦，干脆不看手机了，反正还有一段距离。这个时候打车的人并不多，他们陆陆续续都上车了，除了我旁边的一位男生。这个时候来了一辆绿色小车，看着像是我叫的那辆，正准备拿行李，这时候旁边的男生径直的走到车那放行李并上车了，心想：好吧，难道我看错了？<br>\r\n疑惑地拿出手机走出门准备对车牌号，只见那男生又下车，一句句sorry地把行李从车里拿下来。<br>\r\n我面无表情看这在我面前发生的一切，呼，我终于可以上车了。<br>\r\n跟司机简单对话了几句英语后，他直接跟我说中文。惊讶的我，顺带把此前积累的所有消极情绪清空了，在跟他唠嗑的过程中倍感亲切。<br>\r\n他说在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            新生代会讲中文的华人已经很少了，他是家里人要求他学习中文，所以他才讲得那么好。不过，我后来未能遇见更多当地年轻人进行交谈，这个结论无法得到充分论证。但确实，我在入住酒店、问路、就餐等情况下，只要遇到年纪稍大的华人面孔，他们都能用中文交流。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898517628\" data-index=\"5\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">独自一人在新加坡特种兵citywalk</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898517811\">\r\n                                                                                                        顺利办理入住后，把行李寄存在酒店，开始citywalk。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n【打破对一座国家的偏见最好的方式就是身临其境。】<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本来打算随便逛逛的我，在对\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10754.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新加坡\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            这座城市逐渐深入了解后，我贪婪地在有限的时间线上不断塞进一个个想去的地点。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n从我酒店所在的区域说起吧。<br>\r\n不得不说，Taylor Swift经济效应不是说笑的。想起之前看过一张梗图，画面上画着\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10062.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"美国\" target=\"_blank\">美国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            经济的两大支柱是英伟达和Taylor Swift。<br>\r\n在3月的巡回演出期间，附近的所有酒店几乎都涨价了一倍。我大概提前四个月订酒店，以为在半年前只是刚买完演唱会门票的人把酒店的价格推高而已，这时候价格应该会降一点。然而，好一点的酒店已经被订满了，剩下的选择不多。我这家感觉性价比不错，但也要1300多一晚，房间很小，15平左右，而且位置离演唱会场馆有将近5公里。<br>\r\n不过好处在于，它离\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/27870.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"东海\" target=\"_blank\">东海</a>\r\n                                                                                                            岸非常近近，也就是离大海很近，步行到\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/27870.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"东海\" target=\"_blank\">东海</a>\r\n                                                                                                            岸公园只需要13分钟。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898440798\" data-seq=\"1898440799\" data-pid=\"1898440798\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898440798.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 907px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ec/62c31d69c353530704c1d12c2b10c768.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ec/62c31d69c353530704c1d12c2b10c768.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5d/ec/62c31d69c353530704c1d12c2b10c768.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898440798\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898440796\" data-seq=\"1898440797\" data-pid=\"1898440796\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10097/scenery_24514198/1898440796.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7b/b6/61626eafc9ad51418477a89316a65ddb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7b/b6/61626eafc9ad51418477a89316a65ddb.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7b/b6/61626eafc9ad51418477a89316a65ddb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898440796\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898517955\">\r\n                                                                                                        这一带大部分都是住宅或者餐厅，以别墅为主，高楼大厦在这里反而显得突兀。<br>\r\n清晨七时半，天刚破晓，厚重的云层笼罩天空，挡住了阳光的光辉。走了一会，却见太阳在远方徐徐升起，橙色的光芒穿透云层，在墙上投下斑斓的印记。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n\r\n                                    </div>",
