 data-pid=\"1897749347\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897749347.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/27/75/40b2b722672878e6747ea66a91a16186.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/27/75/40b2b722672878e6747ea66a91a16186.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/27/75/40b2b722672878e6747ea66a91a16186.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897749347\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897749335\" data-seq=\"1897749336\" data-pid=\"1897749335\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897749335.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/82/83/b979ac3a8b4591528df622397dbc892a.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/82/83/b979ac3a8b4591528df622397dbc892a.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/82/83/b979ac3a8b4591528df622397dbc892a.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897749335\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897749351\" data-seq=\"1897749352\" data-pid=\"1897749351\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897749351.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/88/a76e4ebc61a79acd06fe8f6380da5ecf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/88/a76e4ebc61a79acd06fe8f6380da5ecf.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/87/88/a76e4ebc61a79acd06fe8f6380da5ecf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897749351\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897770186\">\r\n                                                                                                        很喜欢这种道路，车来人往，两边高耸入云的树木遮阳挡月，漫步其中，不计过往，不念未来，我只是当下的我。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n                                <div class=\"video_wrapper _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897749386\">\r\n            <div class=\"add_video _j_seqitem \" data-vid=\"3563462\" data-seq=\"1897749386\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3563462?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D&amp;type=.m3u8\" data-type=\"2\" data-ready=\"1\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-audit=\"0\"><video data-type=\"2\" width=\"680\" height=\"auto\" data-url=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/3563462?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22jump%22%7D\" class=\"_js_videojs_hls\" data-noneedinit=\"0\" controls=\"\" src=\"blob:https://www.mafengwo.cn/f5b6facd-7dd3-4843-9f42-29b9ca0792ac\"></video></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        \r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1896773114\">\r\n                                                                                                        明孝陵<br>\r\n始建于明洪武十四年（1381年），是明太祖朱元璋与孝慈高皇后的合葬陵寝，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            最大的帝王陵寝之一。<br>\r\n明孝陵的主体建筑和石刻有\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/140562.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"方城\" target=\"_blank\">方城</a>\r\n                                                                                                            、明楼、宝城、宝顶，包括下马坊、大\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/25339.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"金门\" target=\"_blank\">金门</a>\r\n                                                                                                            、神功圣德碑、神道、石像路石刻等&nbsp;。明孝陵代表了明初建筑和石刻艺术的最高成就，在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            帝陵发展史上有着特殊的地位。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n神道\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897774892\" data-seq=\"1897774893\" data-pid=\"1897774892\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897774892.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4d/0a/e6224a2f79e9b267aec0ff6643320fa8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4d/0a/e6224a2f79e9b267aec0ff6643320fa8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4d/0a/e6224a2f79e9b267aec0ff6643320fa8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897774892\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897774996\" data-seq=\"1897774997\" data-pid=\"1897774996\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897774996.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/ab/77f6bcac02ab09f45fccbae945ac504c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/ab/77f6bcac02ab09f45fccbae945ac504c.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/44/ab/77f6bcac02ab09f45fccbae945ac504c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897774996\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897774868\" data-seq=\"1897774869\" data-pid=\"1897774868\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897774868.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5a/7a/dcba2adf6211f06f6e265bc611b62e38.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5a/7a/dcba2adf6211f06f6e265bc611b62e38.jpeg?imageV