                                     铜牛灯\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898031770\" data-seq=\"1898031771\" data-pid=\"1898031770\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898031770.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ee/90/0e20445a56a73d218f98be9157edc195.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ee/90/0e20445a56a73d218f98be9157edc195.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ee/90/0e20445a56a73d218f98be9157edc195.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898031770\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898031768\" data-seq=\"1898031769\" data-pid=\"1898031768\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898031768.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/16/4c/3032fed71e2857b6220f48dbcef311bf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/16/4c/3032fed71e2857b6220f48dbcef311bf.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/16/4c/3032fed71e2857b6220f48dbcef311bf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898031768\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898357120\">\r\n                                                                                                        错银铜牛灯文创\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898031772\" data-seq=\"1898031773\" data-pid=\"1898031772\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898031772.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c3/e9/b9a86ad6457da303c68e180f5698c2d7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c3/e9/b9a86ad6457da303c68e180f5698c2d7.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c3/e9/b9a86ad6457da303c68e180f5698c2d7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898031772\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898422157\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/55434.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"邳州\" target=\"_blank\">邳州</a>\r\n                                                                                                              汉画石像石墓\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898031700\" data-seq=\"1898031701\" data-pid=\"1898031700\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898031700.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/bb/97/8c0bbb5cbdff09a438646b9d17471eda.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/bb/97/8c0bbb5cbdff09a438646b9d17471eda.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/bb/97/8c0bbb5cbdff09a438646b9d17471eda.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898031700\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898031689\" data-seq=\"1898031690\" data-pid=\"1898031689\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898031689.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/a0/8e934a4e306e335d68a75ba953755aa5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/a0/8e934a4e306e335d68a75ba953755aa5.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/a0/8e934a4e306e335d68a75ba953755aa5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898031689\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898031774\">\r\n                                                                                                        4展厅：六朝迭兴  隋唐华彩<br>\r\n公元三至六世纪，吴、东晋、宋、齐、梁、陈六国相继在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            建都，史称“六朝”。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898430010\" data-index=\"10\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">唐三彩</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898430013\">\r\n                                                                                                        “唐三彩”是唐代低温彩色铅釉陶的通称，始创于唐代早期，在唐玄宗的开元年间达到鼎盛。（后期去\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10195.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西安\" target=\"_blank\">西安</a>\r\n                                                                                                            博物院再做详细介绍）<br>\r\n三彩骆驼俑——身上搭挂着兽面纹饰的驮囊，兽面獠牙外露，眼睛大睁，驮囊里货物和水壶也\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/140671.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"都安\" target=\"_blank\">都安</a>\r\n                                                                                                            放就位。骆驼引颈张口，后肢直立，前腿略弯，牢牢地站立在四方形的踏板上。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898430322\" data-seq=\"1898430323\" data-pid=\"1898430322\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898430322.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1021px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2a/d3/c6ac62d3d603282d12cb4e8dea3fcf71.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2a/d3/c6ac62d3d603282d12cb4e8dea3fcf71.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2a/d3/c6ac62d3d603282d12cb4e8dea3fcf71.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898430322\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898430340\">\r\n                                                                                                        三彩双头瓶——此瓶塑成腹部相对的双鱼形，鱼口即瓶口，双脊即为双系，尾部制成瓶底，鱼目、鱼鳞、鱼鳍一应俱全，表面挂有绿、黄、褐三色釉，三色互相浸润交融。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898431350\" data-seq=\"1898431351\" data-pid=\"1898431350\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898431350.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2f/58/b7cc3b5b46f6c6632bb2341f2628634d.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2f/58/b7cc3b5b46f6c6632bb2341f2628634d.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2f/58/b7cc3b5b46f6c6632bb2341f2628634d.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898431350\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898432980\">\r\n                                                                                                        三彩武士踏兽陶俑\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898343050\" data-seq=\"1898343051\" data-pid=\"1898343050\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898343050.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/66/bb785348ffe127de7fe1f734bedb0549.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/66/bb785348ffe127de7fe1f734bedb0549.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/66/bb785348ffe127de7fe1f734bedb0549.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898343050\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898455634\">\r\n                                                                                                        画彩扬蹄陶马、镇墓兽\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898343052\" data-seq=\"1898343326\" data-pid=\"1898343052\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898343052.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5a/42/db6ac173cf38269b7448fa95edb772f8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5a/42/db6ac173cf38269b7448fa95edb772f8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5a/42/db6ac173cf38269b7448fa95edb772f8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898343052\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898343329\" data-seq=\"1898345935\" data-pid=\"1898343329\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898343329.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f1/df/d860b86f29545212302285cd628da4a8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f1/df/d860b86f29545212302285cd628da4a8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f1/df/d860b86f29545212302285cd628da4a8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898343329\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898066228\" data-index=\"11\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">贵在肆志，仰慕同趣</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898056934\">\r\n                                                                                                        竹林七贤和荣启期砖雕（自己拍的效果不太好，以下为网图），我国发现最早、保存最好的一副砖画，填补了六朝绘画稀有传世真迹的空白，是禁止出国（境）展览文物之一。<br>\r\n由300多块古墓砖组成，出土时分东西两块，一块为嵇康、阮籍、山涛、王戎四人，另一块为向秀、刘伶、阮咸、荣启期四人。荣启期是早于“七贤”七百多年的春秋时期人物，由于荣启期的性格和“七贤”极为相似，所以砖画中安排荣启期和“七贤”在一起，除了绘画构图上对称的需要外，荣启期更有为“七贤”之楷模的寓意。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898056579\" data-seq=\"1898056580\" data-pid=\"1898056579\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898056579.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 488px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/85/94/2d93e80b218857d701df3758bc46a9ed.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/85/94/2d93e80b218857d701df3758bc46a9ed.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/85/94/2d93e80b218857d701df3758bc46a9ed.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898056579\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898065174\">\r\n                                                                                                        砖画人物造型简练而传神，八人席地而坐，或抚琴啸歌，或颔首倾听，性格特征鲜明，人物之间以树木相隔，完美地体现了对称美学。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n荣启期：他是春秋时期的“遁世之士”，据《列子天瑞》篇记载，孔子游泰山，与鼓琴而歌的荣启期有过一番交谈。孔子认为他是一位自得其乐的“高士”。<br>\r\n把荣启期与七贤画在一起，不仅达起到平衡构图的作用，还寓意竹林七贤与古代高人逸士的人文追求一脉相承。画面上七贤均坐姿散漫，赤脚露腿，而荣启期披发长须，腰系绳索，盘腿端坐，双手抚琴，形象较为庄重。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898057079\" data-seq=\"1898057080\" data-pid=\"1898057079\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898057079.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 753px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/19/a0/5988b4b598faa7649281adb4b11e70b7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/19/a0/5988b4b598faa7649281adb4b11e70b7.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/19/a0/5988b4b598faa7649281adb4b11e70b7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898057079\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898067542\">\r\n                                                                                                        阮咸：阮籍的侄子，喜欢饮酒。《晋书．阮咸传》说他“妙解音律，善弹琵琶。”。他弹的是一种长柄、圆肚、四弦的古琵琶，据说由他本人创制，乐器的名字就叫“阮咸”，简称“阮”。弹奏时，形象优雅，如同“明月入怀”。<br>\r\n画面中，阮咸正盘腿坐在树下，专心地弹奏着因他而命名的“阮”。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898057083\" data-seq=\"1898057084\" data-pid=\"1898057083\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898057083.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 754px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/d8/ac29aa03da23067b47d2daaab9d9446e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/d8/ac29aa03da23067b47d2daaab9d9446e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/d8/ac29aa03da23067b47d2daaab9d9446e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898057083\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898068048\">\r\n                                                                                                        刘伶：\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            历史上最有名的“酒鬼”。他作《酒德颂》一文，成为千古名篇。《晋书．刘伶传》说他“止则操巵（zhī，同“卮”，古代酒器）执觚（gū，盛酒酒具），支则挈搕（kē，敲，碰的意思）提壶”，嗜酒如命，大杯小盅，来者不辞。<br>\r\n刘伶，名字有点破损，画面中一副酒徒的摸样：眼睛直盯手中的酒杯，另一只手蘸酒品尝，神情十分专注。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898057085\" data-seq=\"1898057086\" data-pid=\"1898057085\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898057085.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 766px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8b/76/82060e2e71a22fcb58e6c532a49260fc.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8b/76/82060e2e71a22fcb58e6c532a49260fc.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8b/76/82060e2e71a22fcb58e6c532a49260fc.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898057085\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898067604\">\r\n                                                                                                        向秀：是一位书生，魏晋之际有名的学者。他喜欢和嵇康一起打铁，嵇康掌锤，向秀鼓风，两人配合默契。《晋书．向秀传》说他“雅好老庄之学，庄周著内外数十篇……秀乃为之隐解，读之者超然心悟，莫不自足一时也”。<br>\r\n画面上的向秀，倚靠在银杏树边，一肩裸露，闭目沉思。其苦思冥想的神态，似乎正在解读老庄。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898057089\" data-seq=\"1898057090\" data-pid=\"1898057089\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898057089.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 761px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/48/9b/d4d08ae5deb913b9157baa129b6292ce.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/48/9b/d4d08ae5deb913b9157baa129b6292ce.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/48/9b/d4d08ae5deb913b9157baa129b6292ce.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898057089\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898066067\">\r\n                                                                                                        嵇康：“竹林七贤”中的灵魂人物，身材魁伟，容貌俊美，性格孤僻，才华横溢。死前从容弹了一曲《广陵散》，成为千古绝唱。<br>\r\n画中嵇康头梳双髻，膝盖上置一架古琴，正在弹琴。他的神态伟岸孤傲，目光注视着遥远的天际，正是嵇康诗句中“目送归鸿，手挥五弦”的形象。嵇康身旁的银杏和松树，姿态特别优美，似乎配合着琴声随风起舞。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898057097\" data-seq=\"1898057098\" data-pid=\"1898057097\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898057097.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 771px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/26/58/5efbba679dda88032827fb7c5149918d.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/26/58/5efbba679dda88032827fb7c5149918d.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/26/58/5efbba679dda88032827fb7c5149918d.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898057097\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898066494\">\r\n                                                                                                        阮籍：嵇康的莫逆之交。《晋书·阮籍传》描述他“嗜酒能啸”，《世说新语》说他酒后纵兴“长啸”、“韵响嘹亮”。他写了八十二首《咏怀诗》，以晦涩的文字表达了他对现实的绝望。<br>\r\n画中的阮籍，盘膝坐在阔叶竹下，高卷袖子，神态潇洒，他的右手放在唇边，微仰头颅，噘嘴鼓腮，似乎正在长啸。画面抓住了阮籍“嗜酒能啸”的特点，简练传神。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898057095\" data-seq=\"1898057096\" data-pid=\"1898057095\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898057095.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 762px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8a/2f/40c647b02d0f1d8781fbc47380c2ce4b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8a/2f/40c647b02d0f1d8781fbc47380c2ce4b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8a/2f/40c647b02d0f1d8781fbc47380c2ce4b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898057095\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898066800\">\r\n                                                                                                        山涛：“竹林七贤”中年龄最大者。《晋书·山涛传》说他“饮酒至八斗方醉”。<br>\r\n画面上，山涛坐在柳树和槐树之间，头戴布巾，左手端酒，右手拉着左腕的袖子，似乎在敬酒，神态从容而优雅。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898057100\" data-seq=\"1898057101\" data-pid=\"1898057100\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898057100.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 748px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/58/78/0349a76bae8aa4aacbf12cbf366f41eb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/58/78/0349a76bae8aa4aacbf12cbf366f41eb.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/58/78/0349a76bae8aa4aacbf12cbf366f41eb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898057100\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898067436\">\r\n                                                                                                        王戎：“竹林七贤”里的小弟，比山涛小二十九岁。《世说新语》记载，他家有万贯，但非常吝啬。<br>\r\n画面上，王戎坐在银杏和柳树中间，跷着脚，斜身靠一钱箱，一手摆弄着如意，正是庾信《对酒歌》中“王戎舞如意”的写照，可谓细妙。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898057102\" data-seq=\"1898057103\" data-pid=\"1898057102\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898057102.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 766px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7d/81/330cf834bb94e74c0addf0c5fc44d515.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7d/81/330cf834bb94e74c0addf0c5fc44d515.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7d/81/330cf834bb94e74c0addf0c5fc44d515.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898057102\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898020828\">\r\n                                                                                                        5展厅：江淮多姿  宋淮气象<br>\r\n“苏湖熟，天下足”<br>\r\n元代，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10128.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"扬州\" target=\"_blank\">扬州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            是“十二省治所之一”，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"苏州\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            、\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/84589.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"松江\" target=\"_blank\">松江</a>\r\n                                                                                                            成为全国的丝织业和棉纺业中心，仅\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            城内的丝织工匠就多达两万人。文人书画艺术勃兴，出现了黄公望、倪瓒等一代大师，影响深远。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898021139\" data-seq=\"1898021140\" data-pid=\"1898021139\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898021139.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 201px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/56/42/da81a2237eadb6cbbf5fc8bb47b71fee.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/56/42/da81a2237eadb6cbbf5fc8bb47b71fee.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/56/42/da81a2237eadb6cbbf5fc8bb47b71fee.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898021139\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898021141\">\r\n                                                                                                        6展厅：盛世\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/23934.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"江南\" target=\"_blank\">江南</a>\r\n                                                                                                              明清辉煌<br>\r\n明清时期，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的城墙、宫殿、寺庙和\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/23934.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"江南\" target=\"_blank\">江南</a>\r\n                                                                                                            园林等建筑技术及造船业居于全国前列；\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14387.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"江苏\" target=\"_blank\">江苏</a>\r\n                                                                                                            成为全国的书画中心，名家辈出，精品纷呈，领袖画坛；文学创作鼎盛，涌现出施耐庵、吴承恩、曹雪芹等一代大师；\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14387.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"江苏\" target=\"_blank\">江苏</a>\r\n                                                                                                            还是全国工艺中心之一，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            云锦、\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10446.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"宜兴\" target=\"_blank\">宜兴</a>\r\n                                                                                                            紫砂、\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10128.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"扬州\" target=\"_blank\">扬州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            漆器、\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"苏州\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            玉器、刺绣等领全国之风骚。<br>\r\n明   大报恩寺塔琉璃拱门（国家宝藏看到的完整拱门，博物院只看到了零部件）\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898422427\" data-seq=\"1898422428\" data-pid=\"1898422427\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898422427.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/12/9f/7a288c0fa5e6b831e538756cf834e55b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/12/9f/7a288c0fa5e6b831e538756cf834e55b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/12/9f/7a288c0fa5e6b831e538756cf834e55b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898422427\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898422409\" data-seq=\"1898422429\" data-pid=\"1898422409\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898422409.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e1/82/df516b4ad2a14aab16492ec5ef9668bc.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e1/82/df516b4ad2a14aab16492ec5ef9668bc.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e1/82/df516b4ad2a14aab16492ec5ef9668bc.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898422409\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898422784\">\r\n                                                                                                        明代工匠在建造大报恩寺时，重要的建筑构件烧制1～2套备份，主要用来，修复建筑时使用。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898346146\" data-seq=\"1898422420\" data-pid=\"1898346146\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898346146.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c9/6c/5c98fc4a4af5dede439c3bcec0f081fe.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c9/6c/5c98fc4a4af5dede439c3bcec0f081fe.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c9/6c/5c98fc4a4af5dede439c3bcec0f081fe.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898346146\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898346133\" data-seq=\"1898422423\" data-pid=\"1898346133\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898346133.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/cd/65/c0aebaaa1d95c7ccaaa7c3610de42cf2.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/cd/65/c0aebaaa1d95c7ccaaa7c3610de42cf2.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/cd/65/c0aebaaa1d95c7ccaaa7c3610de42cf2.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898346133\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898021461\" data-index=\"12\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">2.特展馆</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898021462\">\r\n                                                                                                        主要用于举办国内外精品展览和院藏宫廷文物为主的专题展。它不仅展示了\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"南京\" target=\"_blank\">南京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            博物院的镇院之宝，还定期举办各种临时展览，吸引众多艺术和历史爱好者。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898021620\" data-seq=\"1898021621\" data-pid=\"1898021620\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898021620.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 824px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f7/1b/dfee76110deb5c6b3bbeb5794f10a5c7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f7/1b/dfee76110deb5c6b3bbeb5794f10a5c7.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f7/1b/dfee76110deb5c6b3bbeb5794f10a5c7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898021620\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898056436\" data-index=\"13\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">不可一日无此君</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898021715\">\r\n                                                                                                        9展厅，也称镇院之宝展厅。<br>\r\n镇院之宝有金兽、明洪武釉里红岁寒三友纹梅瓶、竹林七贤砖画、金蝉玉叶，每段时期的镇院之宝都不同，来这个展厅就像开盲盒。<br>\r\n我的盲盒是梅瓶。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898021384\">\r\n                                                                                                        明洪武  釉里红  岁寒三友  纹梅瓶<br>\r\n现存唯一一件带盖子而且保存完整的洪武釉里红梅瓶。<br>\r\n此梅瓶造型优美，器型完整无缺，岁寒三友指松树、绿竹、梅花三种常绿植物，象征着高洁的志向。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897988145\" data-seq=\"1897988146\" data-pid=\"1897988145\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897988145.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/ac/a29b3850766d42cbe2362fb2896e7b35.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/ac/a29b3850766d42cbe2362fb2896e7b35.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e7/ac/a29b3850766d42cbe2362fb2896e7b35.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897988145\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897990511\">\r\n                                                                                                        瓶浅足沙底，盖成铎形，釉质细腻，虽釉里红发色欠佳，窑变黑色，但瑕不掩瑜。瓶身装饰有七组图案组成，颈上蕉叶纹，肩部纹饰三道（如意云、卷草、缠枝菊花）正中以岁寒三友图为主题，夹饰芭蕉、山石，花卉下绘波涛海水纹，胫部仰莲一周。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897988133\" data-seq=\"1897988134\" data-pid=\"1897988133\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897988133.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/81/cb/3e429f8c2fe1afc042fff182c4635f21.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/81/cb/3e429f8c2fe1afc042fff182c4635f21.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/81/cb/3e429f8c2fe1afc042fff182c4635f21.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897988133\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897988151\" data-seq=\"1897988152\" data-pid=\"1897988151\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1897988151.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b4/0e/8a71c870d19dc28bf6760c43039907f7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b4/0e/8a71c870d19dc28bf6760c43039907f7.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b4/0e/8a71c870d19dc28bf6760c43039907f7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897988151\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898426039\">\r\n                                                                                                        金兽（图片来源于网络），西汉出土的最重最大金器，含金量高达99%，展现了古代金属铸造工艺和金器锤击工艺的完美结合。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898426037\" data-seq=\"1898426038\" data-pid=\"1898426037\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898426037.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1209px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/43/0c568b896913e84a52e23adf2455f42b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/43/0c568b896913e84a52e23adf2455f42b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/43/0c568b896913e84a52e23adf2455f42b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898426037\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898426132\">\r\n                                                                                                        金蝉玉叶（图片来自于网络），金蝉含金量达95%，蝉体形象逼真，玉叶采取\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13061.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新疆\" target=\"_blank\">新疆</a>\r\n                                                                                <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18005.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"和田\" target=\"_blank\">和田</a>\r\n                                                                                                            羊脂玉，孤品。<br>\r\n美的不可方物\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898426034\" data-seq=\"1898426035\" data-pid=\"1898426034\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898426034.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1208px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/89/ea/71e069673901d68460cd1a600b88fd4c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/89/ea/71e069673901d68460cd1a600b88fd4c.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/89/ea/71e069673901d68460cd1a600b88fd4c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898426034\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1897995160\" data-index=\"14\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">走近佛前</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898021856\">\r\n                                                                                                        10展厅（常设）：院藏佛像展<br>\r\n清代帝王和皇室\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143381.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"崇信\" target=\"_blank\">崇信</a>\r\n                                                                                                            藏传佛教，皇宫和皇家苑囿中都设置佛堂，供奉着各种各样的佛龛、佛塔、佛阁、佛像、七珍\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/142386.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"八宝\" target=\"_blank\">八宝</a>\r\n                                                                                                            等佛教供器，尤以佛像为多。佛像有泥、石、木、金铜等多种材质，其中金铜佛像形制规整，比例精确，制作精工，堪称艺术珍品展。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898423785\">\r\n                                                                                                        鎏金释迦牟尼铜像、鎏金药师佛铜像\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898356433\" data-seq=\"1898356434\" data-pid=\"1898356433\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898356433.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 866px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/f4/2878e437d738ac24346c8ca54154654e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/f4/2878e437d738ac24346c8ca54154654e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/f4/2878e437d738ac24346c8ca54154654e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898356433\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898356427\" data-seq=\"1898356428\" data-pid=\"1898356427\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898356427.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e8/7f/dcb49b794d5b07cabd0c46599f6b9198.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstr