ord_mdd\" data-kw=\"和龙\" target=\"_blank\">和龙</a>\r\n                                                                                                            纹滴水\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898346157\" data-seq=\"1898348287\" data-pid=\"1898346157\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898346157.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/55/51/41ecf5b23fa1d173461bf73fcfbef3bb.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/55/51/41ecf5b23fa1d173461bf73fcfbef3bb.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898346157\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898348420\">\r\n                                                                                                        汉  绿釉陶猪圈\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898346161\" data-seq=\"1898348290\" data-pid=\"1898346161\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898346161.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/14/fa/45077348bb49c64da1caa213348ef7a1.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/14/fa/45077348bb49c64da1caa213348ef7a1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898346161\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898348405\">\r\n                                                                                                        历代雕塑<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144942.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"清道\" target=\"_blank\">清道</a>\r\n                                                                                                            光  山水牧牛水池雕瓷\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898346169\" data-seq=\"1898348291\" data-pid=\"1898346169\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898346169.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/19/2b/d876de38ba8047c1bc1938edcf82c0f0.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/19/2b/d876de38ba8047c1bc1938edcf82c0f0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898346169\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898455623\">\r\n                                                                                                        清晚期   象牙镂雕群仙祝寿纹大瓶<br>\r\n此件象牙大瓶器型硕大，盖钮雕刻仕女童子，绕颈一周刻众多仙姑，瓶身满刻亭台楼阁、云彩、树石、人物，组成一幅生动的群仙祝寿画面。雕刻细密谨严，以极繁琐之手法来表现雕琢之能事。此类题材看似表现自由逍遥享乐的神仙世界，其实更象热闹繁华的市井生活。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898355385\" data-seq=\"1898355386\" data-pid=\"1898355385\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898355385.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/52/54/bbb6e8e63909ab5ac4b81e8dc6339cf3.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/52/54/bbb6e8e63909ab5ac4b81e8dc6339cf3.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898355385\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898356052\">\r\n                                                                                                        清   红木雕苦行僧<br>\r\n用整块红木圆雕出一位正在清修的梵像老者的形象，全身无衣遮体、双目深陷，肌骨嶙峋，作低头冥思状。雕像身体骨骼部位表达明晰，加上打磨功夫细腻温润，使得整个人物立体感很强，如真人一般。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898342857\" data-seq=\"1898355445\" data-pid=\"1898342857\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898342857.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/83/3e/01f02739140fc64aa6a87aa4524dd1d5.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/83/3e/01f02739140fc64aa6a87aa4524dd1d5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898342857\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898342867\" data-seq=\"1898355393\" data-pid=\"1898342867\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898342867.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/76/efdf796dd977fbbe3e609c3e99638110.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/76/efdf796dd977fbbe3e609c3e99638110.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898342867\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898342863\" data-seq=\"1898355392\" data-pid=\"1898342863\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898342863.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ca/7c/fb10f0fd5e69946c785194d25b32ecca.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ca/7c/fb10f0fd5e69946c785194d25b32ecca.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ca/7c/fb10f0fd5e69946c785194d25b32ecca.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898342863\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898427002\">\r\n                                                                                                        战国   青铜错银四羊盒\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898346110\" data-seq=\"1898355394\" data-pid=\"1898346110\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898346110.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/31/96/4f7d7a4e684506502fbc3ceb2294d693.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/31/96/4f7d7a4e684506502fbc3ceb2294d693.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/31/96/4f7d7a4e684506502fbc3ceb2294d693.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898346110\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897956911\">\r\n                                                                                                        战国&nbsp; 髹漆镇墓兽<br>\r\n典型的战国楚文化镇墓兽，一般由三部分组成：鹿角、头和底座。一般认为鹿角象征防御，可能是当时认为可以使墓主人免受鬼的侵扰；头像猛兽又像蛇，是借用它们的形象来厌胜辟邪；底座凸显出九个方块，可能用来象征\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10601.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"九州\" target=\"_blank\">九州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            和大地，也有人认为是象征人死后居住的地方——幽都。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898345951\" data-seq=\"1898355397\" data-pid=\"1898345951\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898345951.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/62/e0/693ee577e891092d42b7079423330a75.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/62/e0/693ee577e891092d42b7079423330a75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/62/e0/693ee577e891092d42b7079423330a75.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898345951\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898427056\">\r\n                                                                                                        汉   彩绘陶灯\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898345945\" data-seq=\"1898355403\" data-pid=\"1898345945\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898345945.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/82/f8/67e8f1f228883912a39c13853b11b603.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/82/f8/67e8f1f228883912a39c13853b11b603.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/82/f8/67e8f1f228883912a39c13853b11b603.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898345945\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898405221\">\r\n                                                                                                        清   人物砖雕门楼\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898342927\" data-seq=\"1898355399\" data-pid=\"1898342927\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898342927.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b2/5f/db90265ecb60d680fe273843b5f5106e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b2/5f/db90265ecb60d680fe273843b5f5106e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b2/5f/db90265ecb60d680fe273843b5f5106e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898342927\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898356102\">\r\n                                                                                                        清   \r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64559.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"德化\" target=\"_blank\">德化</a>\r\n                                                                                                            窑送子观音瓷塑\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898342871\" data-seq=\"1898355430\" data-pid=\"1898342871\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898342871.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a3/63/cbc3b9c5b17b3349cb6b1a3a5cc4dc97.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a3/63/cbc3b9c5b17b3349cb6b1a3a5cc4dc97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a3/63/cbc3b9c5b17b3349cb6b1a3a5cc4dc97.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898342871\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898426922\">\r\n                                                                                                        明   石雕黑财神\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898342861\" data-seq=\"1898355431\" data-pid=\"1898342861\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898342861.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a2/f6/50d5f8ea3e451835a711635ec8381ea2.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a2/f6/50d5f8ea3e451835a711635ec8381ea2.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a2/f6/50d5f8ea3e451835a711635ec8381ea2.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898342861\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897968013\">\r\n                                                                                                        清   吉神八仙彩绘砖雕\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898355441\" data-seq=\"1898355442\" data-pid=\"1898355441\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898355441.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/df/5a/5e67517e2b3469776ddf471b7f165fbd.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/df/5a/5e67517e2b3469776ddf471b7f165fbd.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898355441\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898426867\">\r\n                                                                                                        清   彩绘四世同堂石刻\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898355443\" data-seq=\"1898355444\" data-pid=\"1898355443\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898355443.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/52/df25e0cdef824eac7822a2afc28831ef.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/52/df25e0cdef824eac7822a2afc28831ef.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/52/df25e0cdef824eac7822a2afc28831ef.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898355443\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898427192\">\r\n                                                                                                        汉   青铜摇钱树\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898355436\" data-seq=\"1898355437\" data-pid=\"1898355436\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898355436.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/54/f8/2fe03d4c7cda804a966a8a8513fdba84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/54/f8/2fe03d4c7cda804a966a8a8513fdba84.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898355436\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897877108\">\r\n                                                                                                        清   汉\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10638.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"白玉\" target=\"_blank\">白玉</a>\r\n                                                                                                            雕三国屏风\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898342892\" data-seq=\"1898355448\" data-pid=\"1898342892\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898342892.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/61/37/84d0a789de50b536cdbb2c2bf1f728b4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/61/37/84d0a789de50b536cdbb2c2bf1f728b4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898342892\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898355404\">\r\n                                                                                                        清&nbsp; “海屋添筹”\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/140760.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"祁阳\" target=\"_blank\">祁阳</a>\r\n                                                                                                            石插屏\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898429720\" data-seq=\"1898429721\" data-pid=\"1898429720\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898429720.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3e/aa/7c828c3ab3461bab882276b8094a3251.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3e/aa/7c828c3ab3461bab882276b8094a3251.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898429720\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898429722\">\r\n                                                                                                        吴为山雕塑没看成，还挺遗憾。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898448854\" data-index=\"21\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t1\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">赏心乐事——赏缂丝胤禛十二美人图</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898434643\">\r\n                                                                                                        织于至善——罗关根缂丝作品展（临时展）<br>\r\n缂丝是一种\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            传统丝织品，其工艺特色是以缂织方式织造，纬线并不贯穿全幅作品，而仅在需要处与经线交织，以生蚕丝为经线，彩色熟丝为纬线，采用通经回纬的方法织成的平纹织。即纬丝按照预先描绘的图案，不贯通全幅，用多把小梭子按图案色彩分别挖织，使织物上花纹与素地、色与色之间呈现一些断痕，类似刀刻的形象，这便是“通经断纬”法。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"苏州\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            缂丝画也与\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10156.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"杭州\" target=\"_blank\">杭州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            丝织画、\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/38611.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"永春\" target=\"_blank\">永春</a>\r\n                                                                                                            纸织画、\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12703.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"四川\" target=\"_blank\">四川</a>\r\n                                                                                                            竹帘画并称为\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的“四大家织”。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898434882\">\r\n                                                                                                        缂丝的工艺\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898434828\" data-seq=\"1898434829\" data-pid=\"1898434828\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898434828.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/26/c82d4e2ce3897bdf45a26d171cb61f61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/26/c82d4e2ce3897bdf45a26d171cb61f61.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898434828\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898434917\">\r\n                                                                                                        罗关根先生捐赠的缂丝作品《胤禛十二美人图》，结合院藏宋代至明清时期的部分缂丝作品，介绍缂丝的独特工艺，让人们直观感受传统工艺的魅力，呈现至善至美的工匠精神。<br>\r\n《胤禛十二美人图》原作描绘了十二位身着汉服的宫廷女子品茶、观书、对镜、赏蝶等恬静闲适的生活场景。（存于故宫博物院）\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898449916\">\r\n                                                                                                        倚塌观鹊、桐荫品茶、观书沉吟\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898434927\" data-seq=\"1898434928\" data-pid=\"1898434927\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898434927.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4c/a2/c66253509d9f32212ff2c1d373904acf.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4c/a2/c66253509d9f32212ff2c1d373904acf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898434927\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898434944\" data-seq=\"1898434945\" data-pid=\"1898434944\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898434944.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2a/88/e438e5b4be05e4b5fec0655e1a128bb0.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2a/88/e438e5b4be05e4b5fec0655e1a128bb0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898434944\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898434949\" data-seq=\"1898434950\" data-pid=\"1898434949\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/10684/scenery_24512015/1898434949.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 905px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/bb/8f/cabfa0367057f38e105725fa67964d98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https:/