  articleList: [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Hohhot！ Hohhot | This \"Qingcheng outside the Saiwai\" is a happy hometown for meat lovers!",
      "descr": "Last month, Brother Xiang was invited to a conference and went to Hohhot, the district capital of Inner Mongolia. Although Brother Xiang has been to Inner Mongolia twice before, he has never set foot in Hohhot.\r\nAs a heavy travel enthusiast, since Brother Xiang has gone out this time, he must take this opportunity to take a good look in Hoh, feel the history and culture of this \"green city outside the city\", and unlock a new food map!",
      "cover": "http://localhost:9090/files/download/11.jpeg",
      "content": "<div class=\"vc_article\">\r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            <div class=\"va_con _j_master_content\" data-cs-t=\"ginfo_kw_hotel\">\r\n    <div class=\"block-loading loading_backward\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"_j_content_box\">\r\n\t        <div data-seq=\"1897495206\" data-index=\"1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">前言</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897936154\">\r\n                                                                                                        上个月，翔哥受邀参加了一个会议，去了一趟\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            区府\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n虽然翔哥以前去过两次\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，但未曾踏足过\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            。<br>\r\n作为一个重度旅行爱好者，翔哥这次既然都出门了，肯定要趁这个机会在呼市好好逛逛，感受一下这座“塞外青城”的历史文化，解锁一片新的美食地图！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898020156\" data-seq=\"1898020157\" data-pid=\"1898020156\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1898020156.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/08/2105861ffbaf8e935d61d8cd689370d9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/08/2105861ffbaf8e935d61d8cd689370d9.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/08/2105861ffbaf8e935d61d8cd689370d9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898020156\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898593299\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            这片广阔的土地，给人的第一印象总是壮丽的美景。从\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11526.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"大兴安岭\" target=\"_blank\">大兴安岭</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的森林，到\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10704.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"锡林郭勒\" target=\"_blank\">锡林郭勒</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的草原，再到\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11577.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"阿拉善\" target=\"_blank\">阿拉善</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的沙漠和胡杨，沿着雄鸡版图的背脊，自西向东勾勒出高低起伏的地貌风光。<br>\r\n但说到自治区首府——\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，远道而来的旅行者大多只会把它当作旅途里的一个中转站，毕竟相比起其它盟市，呼市的自然风光确实略逊一筹。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136602\" data-seq=\"1897136702\" data-pid=\"1897136602\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136602.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/80/fb/589a9d5eb6d78a2d91a9f5de58699c36.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/80/fb/589a9d5eb6d78a2d91a9f5de58699c36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/80/fb/589a9d5eb6d78a2d91a9f5de58699c36.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136602\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898020158\">\r\n                                                                                                        但另一方面，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的人文与历史绝对不可小觑，入主中原的梦想激励马背民族一次次挥鞭南下，与历史上的中原王朝进行了旷日持久的拉锯战，草原文化与中原文化在这里彼此感染。<br>\r\n从战国时期的云中郡到北魏的盛乐城，再从辽代的丰洲城到明清时期的归化与绥远，这座拥有两千多年建城史的城市至今留下了众多的历史遗迹，它的底蕴深厚得远远超出你的想象，值得花时间去感受！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135362\" data-seq=\"1897135443\" data-pid=\"1897135362\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135362.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/18/55/6624a884f167ebc85b11a14cc27b3905.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/18/55/6624a884f167ebc85b11a14cc27b3905.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/18/55/6624a884f167ebc85b11a14cc27b3905.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135362\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898020603\">\r\n                                                                                                        不仅如此，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            还是一个美食天堂！随着“走西口”为\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            带来了大量的晋陕移民，牛羊肉与碳水在这里碰撞出了豪放的食谱。<br>\r\n这里有涮羊肉、烤羊排、手把肉和羊杂碎，如果你是肉食爱好者，那么呼市绝对是你的快乐老家！这里还有稍麦、莜面、焖面、炸糕和酿皮这样的碳水炸弹，以及琳琅满目的奶制品，点菜的时候只怪肚子太小！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898022959\" data-seq=\"1898022960\" data-pid=\"1898022959\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:640px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1898022959.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 426px; width: 640px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ee/95/6dc6ae2138ea02b0078653211bf883fd.gif?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ee/95/6dc6ae2138ea02b0078653211bf883fd.gif?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ee/95/6dc6ae2138ea02b0078653211bf883fd.gif?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898022959\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898778766\">\r\n                                                                                                        与翔哥以往的游记一样，这篇游记分为两个部分：前面先说翔哥在呼市吃到美食，后面部分则是介绍呼市的景点。<br>\r\n有需要的话可以根据游记目录，跳转到相应的位置。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1896766195\" data-index=\"2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">预览</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898605925\">\r\n                                                                                                        提起呼市最有名的小吃，非稍麦莫属！<br>\r\n每天清晨，当这个城市醒来的时候，羊肉就会与碳水结合在一起，以稍麦这种豪迈又不失细腻的方式，出现在了当地人的餐桌上。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136600\" data-seq=\"1898601494\" data-pid=\"1897136600\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136600.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a9/99/71a211a2ebc31f97af4e6d433ed90bb8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a9/99/71a211a2ebc31f97af4e6d433ed90bb8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a9/99/71a211a2ebc31f97af4e6d433ed90bb8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136600\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898606110\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            有着全\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            最好吃的羊肉之一，当地流行的冰煮羊火锅，绝对值得一尝！<br>\r\n冰水可以减缓羊肉的受热速度，形成一种类似低温慢煮的效果，从而避免蛋白质硬化和水分流失，更大程度地保留羊肉的风味。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897803339\" data-seq=\"1898601495\" data-pid=\"1897803339\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897803339.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/f9/826b3b78dd7850e683c48afe29a40a7b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/f9/826b3b78dd7850e683c48afe29a40a7b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/f9/826b3b78dd7850e683c48afe29a40a7b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897803339\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898606234\">\r\n                                                                                                        白煮做法的羊肉在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/31808.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西北\" target=\"_blank\">西北</a>\r\n                                                                                                            被称为手抓羊肉，唯独\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            人叫它手把肉——更确切地说是手扒肉，因为传统吃法是用要用手扒着吃。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136592\" data-seq=\"1898601606\" data-pid=\"1897136592\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136592.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4c/dd/6a93e4dc375f5aa20d6d409b40768363.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4c/dd/6a93e4dc375f5aa20d6d409b40768363.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4c/dd/6a93e4dc375f5aa20d6d409b40768363.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136592\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898606288\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10704.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"锡林郭勒\" target=\"_blank\">锡林郭勒</a>\r\n                                                                                                            盟产的苏尼特羊，品质在整个\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            都算得上是天花板。把这种羊骨头拿来清炖，大道至简，却最能突出羊肉本身的鲜香。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137314\" data-seq=\"1898601496\" data-pid=\"1897137314\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137314.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/70/74/cd2425ea2cd2a9f64abcd653c687aff0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/70/74/cd2425ea2cd2a9f64abcd653c687aff0.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/70/74/cd2425ea2cd2a9f64abcd653c687aff0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137314\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898606555\">\r\n                                                                                                        呼市人爱吃羊，羊的任何一个部位都逃不过吃货的法眼。一碗羊杂碎，一个焙子，对肉食爱好者来说，便是最惬意的早餐。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137263\" data-seq=\"1898601497\" data-pid=\"1897137263\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137263.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/e5/05f16c436e08f2f8187018407a89363b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/e5/05f16c436e08f2f8187018407a89363b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ba/e5/05f16c436e08f2f8187018407a89363b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137263\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898606814\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            不仅肉食有名，这里的碳水盛宴也超乎人们的想象。<br>\r\n在呼市能吃到很有地域色彩的莜面莜面窝窝，与\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13033.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"山西\" target=\"_blank\">山西</a>\r\n                                                                                                            人爱趁热浇酱汁不同，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            本地人更喜欢凉拌的吃法。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136643\" data-seq=\"1898601927\" data-pid=\"1897136643\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136643.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/99/13/73f84d6e925e8b8cb4a9e8e2dd68390a.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/99/13/73f84d6e925e8b8cb4a9e8e2dd68390a.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/99/13/73f84d6e925e8b8cb4a9e8e2dd68390a.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136643\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898606983\">\r\n                                                                                                        与其它\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/66113.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西北省\" target=\"_blank\">西北省</a>\r\n                                                                                                            份一样，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            也有吃凉皮的传统，并在习惯上被叫做酿皮——更地道的叫法是“让”皮。河套平原自古是重要的农业产区，挼出来的酿皮自然也就更好吃。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136683\" data-seq=\"1898601776\" data-pid=\"1897136683\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136683.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/03/83/56d8f460100a6e567ed589265dbec815.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/03/83/56d8f460100a6e567ed589265dbec815.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/03/83/56d8f460100a6e567ed589265dbec815.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136683\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898607153\">\r\n                                                                                                        巴盟焖面更像是一种糅合了多地风味的面食，明明都是最普通的食材，却在铁锅里幻化成了意想不到的美味！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137281\" data-seq=\"1898601777\" data-pid=\"1897137281\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137281.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c9/52/adcfa020de7647ba92ce91d483a6d1ce.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c9/52/adcfa020de7647ba92ce91d483a6d1ce.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c9/52/adcfa020de7647ba92ce91d483a6d1ce.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137281\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898607313\">\r\n                                                                                                        北方各省对饸饹的做法，都有各自的绝活。\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            饸饹的传统浇头，通常是卤肉臊加上大块的土豆与豆腐。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135345\" data-seq=\"1898602511\" data-pid=\"1897135345\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135345.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/50/0d/5d98471545e05aa5510e0c29d3dafe7e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/50/0d/5d98471545e05aa5510e0c29d3dafe7e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/50/0d/5d98471545e05aa5510e0c29d3dafe7e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135345\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898607472\">\r\n                                                                                                        当地人的餐桌上，少不了奶制品的身影，当中最常出现的无疑是奶茶。对\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            族人来说，奶茶更像是解腻消食的热汤。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136594\" data-seq=\"1898601948\" data-pid=\"1897136594\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136594.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c0/47/f21cd9e7a47c79808075b09b21209e01.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c0/47/f21cd9e7a47c79808075b09b21209e01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c0/47/f21cd9e7a47c79808075b09b21209e01.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136594\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898607653\">\r\n                                                                                                        奶皮子是牛奶中的精华，是把它泡进奶茶里捞起来吃，浓烈的奶香在嘴里瞬间迸发出来，好吃到爆炸！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137318\" data-seq=\"1898602524\" data-pid=\"1897137318\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137318.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/89/c76ca7103d609c567c063e29f05794d7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/89/c76ca7103d609c567c063e29f05794d7.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/89/c76ca7103d609c567c063e29f05794d7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137318\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898607731\">\r\n                                                                                                        相比起\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            其它盟市，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的确没有别具一格的自然风光，这座城市更精彩的地方显然是在它的历史与文化。<br>\r\n始建于辽代的万部华严经塔，就像是一件宏大的艺术品，塔身的造像和装饰，不仅承袭了盛唐遗风，也融入了不少北地契丹的审美。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137266\" data-seq=\"1898602259\" data-pid=\"1897137266\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137266.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c2/4b/44d362d1d5dba9b2008b3c0f570ad9bf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c2/4b/44d362d1d5dba9b2008b3c0f570ad9bf.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c2/4b/44d362d1d5dba9b2008b3c0f570ad9bf.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137266\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898607953\">\r\n                                                                                                        浩特旧城云集了众多召庙，数百年间香火不断，呼市拥有“召城”的称谓绝非浪得虚名。<br>\r\n由阿拉坦汗亲自主持修建的大召无量寺，是呼市的这些藏传佛教召庙里，历史最悠久也是名气最大的一座。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136607\" data-seq=\"1898602278\" data-pid=\"1897136607\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136607.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4a/74/4d83a57a14cc90e3c987a971644edc18.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4a/74/4d83a57a14cc90e3c987a971644edc18.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4a/74/4d83a57a14cc90e3c987a971644edc18.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136607\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898608529\">\r\n                                                                                                        与大召无量寺一街之隔的席力图召，也是早年归化城的七大召之一。寺里的经堂巧妙结合了藏式与汉式风格，堪称\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的藏汉合璧建筑中最\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64941.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"成功\" target=\"_blank\">成功</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的范例。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136634\" data-seq=\"1898602284\" data-pid=\"1897136634\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136634.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/14/9d/6ead3f7b5af64375f87b48d9d648dbf7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/14/9d/6ead3f7b5af64375f87b48d9d648dbf7.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/14/9d/6ead3f7b5af64375f87b48d9d648dbf7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136634\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898608920\">\r\n                                                                                                        在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的召庙丛林里，相对小众一些的五塔寺，也是一个不该被错过的地方。这里除了有精美夺目的金刚座舍利宝塔，还有一件稀世珍宝：蒙文天文图。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135365\" data-seq=\"1898602260\" data-pid=\"1897135365\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135365.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e6/8c/49188cfe1671c487f1d1c73b828d0ad9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e6/8c/49188cfe1671c487f1d1c73b828d0ad9.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e6/8c/49188cfe1671c487f1d1c73b828d0ad9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135365\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898609475\">\r\n                                                                                                        宝尔汉佛塔的修建时间并不长，却有一个特别响亮的名头：世界第一佛塔！<br>\r\n这座八十米高的佛塔拥有一双“眼睛”，象征着法力无边的佛眼正注视着世上的万物——当你注视佛塔的眼睛时，他也在注视你！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135412\" data-seq=\"1898602261\" data-pid=\"1897135412\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135412.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/71/db/29f65658a0a274c20d22413114a7e76c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/71/db/29f65658a0a274c20d22413114a7e76c.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/71/db/29f65658a0a274c20d22413114a7e76c.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135412\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898609742\">\r\n                                                                                                        自古以来，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            地区就是一个多民族交往交融的文化驿站。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            清真大寺在装饰上凸显伊斯兰教风格，以花卉和几何图案为饰，却又兼容了传统彩绘和砖雕艺术。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136666\" data-seq=\"1898602299\" data-pid=\"1897136666\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136666.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/46/5e/7c32afac9b3c7821de4347a50340cbfe.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/46/5e/7c32afac9b3c7821de4347a50340cbfe.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/46/5e/7c32afac9b3c7821de4347a50340cbfe.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136666\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898609902\">\r\n                                                                                                        距离清真大寺不远的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            天主教堂，也是一座拥有百年历史的老建筑。在圣堂旁边的院子里，还能找到当年西方传教士的墓碑。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136678\" data-seq=\"1898602300\" data-pid=\"1897136678\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136678.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/39/78/d54682747075dcff4887d46d599a3f61.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/39/78/d54682747075dcff4887d46d599a3f61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/39/78/d54682747075dcff4887d46d599a3f61.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136678\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898610061\">\r\n                                                                                                        始建于清乾隆年间的绥远城将军衙署，见证了绥远城将近三百年的历史风云，“一座将军府，半部青城史”，府门匾额上的“漠南第一府”所言不虚！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137299\" data-seq=\"1898602339\" data-pid=\"1897137299\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137299.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/86/3e/04979734c43fbb1bef29a3e0d149c048.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/86/3e/04979734c43fbb1bef29a3e0d149c048.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/86/3e/04979734c43fbb1bef29a3e0d149c048.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137299\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898612663\">\r\n                                                                                                        公主府是清代\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63807.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"和硕\" target=\"_blank\">和硕</a>\r\n                                                                                                            恪靖公主的府第，这个已有三百余年历史的院落仍然精致清丽，室内的展览细细看下来，会对公主的生\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64551.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"平和\" target=\"_blank\">平和</a>\r\n                                                                                                            清代满蒙联姻制度有更深的了解。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n    \r\n        <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137307\" data-seq=\"1898602340\" data-pid=\"1897137307\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137307.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/6f/b8/cbf65e3bb229cc7547947994d20414e2.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/6f/b8/cbf65e3bb229cc7547947994d20414e2.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/6f/b8/cbf65e3bb229cc7547947994d20414e2.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137307\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898612806\">\r\n                                                                                                        事实上，中原王朝统治者与外族和亲的历史由来已久，除了公主府里的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63807.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"和硕\" target=\"_blank\">和硕</a>\r\n                                                                                                            恪靖公主，西汉时期的王昭君更是家喻户晓——俗称“青冢”的昭君墓，就在呼市南郊大\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/22006.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"黑河\" target=\"_blank\">黑河</a>\r\n                                                                                                            畔。<br>\r\n美人远嫁塞外多少有些凄婉，昭君和亲促进了汉朝与匈奴近半个世纪\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/66290.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"和平\" target=\"_blank\">和平</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的故事，却被人们广为传颂。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136653\" data-seq=\"1898602374\" data-pid=\"1897136653\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136653.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/53/ca/24459a921ee7126dcf15e939f3853c56.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/53/ca/24459a921ee7126dcf15e939f3853c56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/53/ca/24459a921ee7126dcf15e939f3853c56.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136653\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898613387\">\r\n                                                                                                        走进\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            博物院，就仿佛打开了厚厚的一本历史书。你在这里能看见自旧石器时代至青铜时代，再到\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            历史上最辉煌的辽代、元代的重要文物，甚至还能看到数亿年前的古生物化石。<br>\r\n馆藏文物总数量超过十五万件，虽然对公众展出的文物只占了很小的一部分，但还是令人眼花缭乱！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135394\" data-seq=\"1898602375\" data-pid=\"1897135394\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135394.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/42/1c/71f34a64b014aea58468b718ee87b862.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/42/1c/71f34a64b014aea58468b718ee87b862.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/42/1c/71f34a64b014aea58468b718ee87b862.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135394\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1896766196\" data-index=\"3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">【呼和浩特 | 美食】</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897858635\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            美食博大精深，蒙餐是一个历史很悠久的菜系，但相比起传统的八大菜系，很多人对蒙餐的概念其实是很模糊的。<br>\r\n实际上，由于\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            地域跨度太大，蒙东五盟的饮食文化已经贴近\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16215.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"东北\" target=\"_blank\">东北</a>\r\n                                                                                                            三省，所以狭义上的蒙餐其实更接近于呼包鄂所在河套地区菜系。<br>\r\n牛羊肉、奶制品和碳水永远是呼市美食的主旋律，同时还因为在历史上进行过“走西口”的人口迁徙，所以呼市美食在传统\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            族饮食文化的基础上融合了不少晋陕风味，构筑出一片独特的风味宇宙！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898026151\" data-seq=\"1898026152\" data-pid=\"1898026151\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1898026151.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a7/1f/a4336eae28dd4da16bd4b443e59c2fef.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a7/1f/a4336eae28dd4da16bd4b443e59c2fef.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a7/1f/a4336eae28dd4da16bd4b443e59c2fef.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898026151\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898026153\">\r\n                                                                                                        下面翔哥就来带你们看看，呼市的美食能有多好吃！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1896766247\" data-index=\"4\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">沁园稍麦</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897503058\">\r\n                                                                            <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            有句话叫“无烧麦，不青城”，若提起呼市最有名的小吃，非稍麦莫属！<br>\r\n每天清晨，当这个城市醒来的时候，羊肉就会与碳水结合在一起，以稍麦这种豪迈又不失细腻的方式，出现在了当地人的餐桌上。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的街头随处可见稍麦馆，甚至还有“稍麦文化一条街”。翔哥这次在呼市打卡了两家稍麦，第一家是五塔寺附近的沁园稍麦，店里食客以附近街坊居民为主，喝茶聊天声此起彼伏。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135354\" data-seq=\"1897135435\" data-pid=\"1897135354\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135354.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/1b/25896f97934b69b08f6b22abc5c6e2b6.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/1b/25896f97934b69b08f6b22abc5c6e2b6.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/1b/25896f97934b69b08f6b22abc5c6e2b6.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135354\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897680557\">\r\n                                                                                                        有意思的是，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的稍麦馆不仅是吃早餐的地方，更像是一个社交场所。许多老呼市人早上起床的第一件事，就是到稍麦馆里喝茶聊天。<br>\r\n稍麦的灵魂伴侣是砖茶，这种发酵过的黑茶最能化解羊肉的油腻。点一笼热气腾腾的烧麦，泡上一壶浓浓的砖茶，边聊天边吃。一口烧麦一口砖茶，是只有本地人才能体会的仪式感。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135355\" data-seq=\"1897135436\" data-pid=\"1897135355\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135355.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/fa/3d/2c6659b69aaa2538730386cc85b00aa9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/fa/3d/2c6659b69aaa2538730386cc85b00aa9.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/fa/3d/2c6659b69aaa2538730386cc85b00aa9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135355\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897504446\">\r\n                                                                                                        当然，早餐的主角还是稍麦。这种以烫面为皮，裹馅上笼蒸熟的面食小吃，在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            南北可谓是百花齐放，不同地域的稍麦馅儿品种繁多，并被冠以稍麦、烧卖、稍梅等名字。<br>\r\n呼市以咸鲜口味为主，最经典的稍麦馅儿是羊肉大葱馅——沁园稍麦只有这一种馅儿，用的是“二肥八瘦”的羊大腿肉，葱也只用葱白。<br>\r\n如果你是初来乍到，要注意\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的稍麦是按两卖的，而且是按稍麦皮重量计算的，呼市稍麦一笼就是一两即八个，这家店可以点半两也就是四个稍麦，很人性化。顺带科普一下，呼市的稍麦以皮薄著称，外市例如\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11574.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"包头\" target=\"_blank\">包头</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的稍麦一两只有六个，显然呼市的稍麦皮要比\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11574.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"包头\" target=\"_blank\">包头</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的更薄！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135357\" data-seq=\"1897135438\" data-pid=\"1897135357\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135357.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/35/58/87f92006a569aa057b158c115041b539.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/35/58/87f92006a569aa057b158c115041b539.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/35/58/87f92006a569aa057b158c115041b539.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135357\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897680653\">\r\n                                                                                                        蒸好的稍麦皮薄如蝉翼，看上去就好像一个挂起来的口袋。呼市人制作稍麦皮是很有讲究的，要用到一种特殊的槌子，擀出来的面皮才能足够薄，包馅儿时也要轻捏不能封口。<br>\r\n夹起一个稍麦，轻薄的皮子拥抱着丰满的馅料，羊肉的味道很浓郁，却没有一丝膻气。为了给稍麦提鲜，馅儿里通常还会加入用亚麻籽榨的胡麻油，羊肉的鲜香在大葱和调料的衬托下，好吃到有点犯规了！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135358\" data-seq=\"1897135439\" data-pid=\"1897135358\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135358.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/0d/18/bf904c00953c21428d61c08aecf23eab.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/0d/18/bf904c00953c21428d61c08aecf23eab.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/0d/18/bf904c00953c21428d61c08aecf23eab.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135358\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897680685\">\r\n                                                                                                        呼市除了有蒸稍麦，还有煎稍麦。煎稍麦的馅儿和蒸稍麦是一样的，在高温热油的淬炼下，底部煎得金黄焦脆非常香，但咬开后，里面的馅儿依然鲜嫩多汁！<br>\r\n蘸着醋和辣椒入口，鲜香的羊肉味道瞬间充满整个口腔，味蕾被充分激发，风卷残云瞬间空盘！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135356\" data-seq=\"1897135437\" data-pid=\"1897135356\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135356.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/c8/e59ed8988b0d4450bcd10b50315acaff.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/c8/e59ed8988b0d4450bcd10b50315acaff.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3c/c8/e59ed8988b0d4450bcd10b50315acaff.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135356\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897688067\">\r\n                                                                                                        吃稍麦的时候，还可以配些店家自制的腊八蒜。这种北方常见的腌制小菜，翠绿的色泽来自于低温和米醋共同作用产生的蒜绿素。<br>\r\n经过米醋的浸泡，蒜的辛辣不再张扬，就着稍麦一块吃或者直接吃，别有一番风味！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135359\" data-seq=\"1897135440\" data-pid=\"1897135359\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135359.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a6/5a/3a45f7376e88bcfc822cdfc828bae1e9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a6/5a/3a45f7376e88bcfc822cdfc828bae1e9.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a6/5a/3a45f7376e88bcfc822cdfc828bae1e9.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135359\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897145937\">\r\n                                                                                                        【沁园稍麦（小召头道巷店）】<br>\r\n地址：\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市玉泉区小召头道巷。<br>\r\n推荐：蒸稍麦、煎稍麦、砖茶。<br>\r\n人均消费：20元。<br>\r\n———————————————\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1896766307\" data-index=\"5\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">德顺源</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897688415\">\r\n                                                                                                        翔哥去的另一家稍麦馆叫德顺源，他们家做的是连锁，分店的数量和规模在呼市数一数二，甚至在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"北京\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>\r\n                                                                                                            都开了分店。我们去的是大盛魁店，位置就在席力图召旁边。<br>\r\n因为德顺源的名气太大了，这家分店又开在景区旁边，在去之前翔哥有点担心他家的出品。但实际体验下来，感觉是满意的。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136596\" data-seq=\"1897136696\" data-pid=\"1897136596\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136596.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2e/f1/f3033ac28172c2d7484de0f6a791fbd4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2e/f1/f3033ac28172c2d7484de0f6a791fbd4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/2e/f1/f3033ac28172c2d7484de0f6a791fbd4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136596\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897690126\">\r\n                                                                                                        与上一家沁园稍麦一样，德顺源的稍麦也是现点现做的，所以要耐心等一会儿。<br>\r\n在等候稍麦上桌的时间里，翔哥查了一下呼市稍麦的起源。实际上，关于这种食物的由来众说纷纭，有人认为早在元代就已经出现，也有说法源自于明末清初，是一家包子铺的改良作品，或者说是在茶馆里“捎带着卖一下”。<br>\r\n但不管怎样，稍麦在清代就已经成为了这片土地的地标美食，时至如今依然是呼市人最熟悉而顽固的故乡味道。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136597\" data-seq=\"1897136697\" data-pid=\"1897136597\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136597.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/18/4c/1c464bb66f25bf3783883d8d03ad564b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/18/4c/1c464bb66f25bf3783883d8d03ad564b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136597\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897686526\">\r\n                                                                                                        德顺源的招牌同样是羊肉大葱稍麦，有了大葱的加持，羊肉不腥不膻。馅儿里有汤汁，吃起来就像灌汤包一样。<br>\r\n外地人第一次吃呼市稍麦，有可能会觉得面皮褶子有点半生。实际上，这种生劲是当地人喜欢的口感，同时不过熟也是为了保持褶子花朵般的造型，假如面皮全熟，则造型全无。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136599\" data-seq=\"1897136699\" data-pid=\"1897136599\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136599.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/9f/fa/f3597ab0e71356f465aed5c3f2c51648.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/9f/fa/f3597ab0e71356f465aed5c3f2c51648.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136599\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897695434\">\r\n                                                                                                        翔哥还尝了他们家的羊肉沙葱稍麦，作为不少南方人的蔬菜盲区，沙葱其实是一种生长在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/31808.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西北\" target=\"_blank\">西北</a>\r\n                                                                                                            地区中、高海拔的野菜。<br>\r\n与别的蔬菜不同，沙葱有一种氤氲扑鼻的特殊香味，能够去腥去膻，与羊肉本身融合得很好，它这种辛香却不辣的香气，带给人眼前一亮的感觉！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136600\" data-seq=\"1897136700\" data-pid=\"1897136600\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136600.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a9/99/71a211a2ebc31f97af4e6d433ed90bb8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a9/99/71a211a2ebc31f97af4e6d433ed90bb8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136600\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897696570\">\r\n                                                                                                        德顺源的煎稍麦也值得一尝，蒸好的羊肉大葱稍麦，在平底煎锅里一煎，稍麦的味道也变得热烈了许多！<br>\r\n顺便提一句，呼市本地人吃稍麦还有一种隐藏吃法，就是用焙子夹着稍麦吃。至于焙子是什么，翔哥先卖个关子，后面说羊杂碎的时候再一起介绍。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136601\" data-seq=\"1897136701\" data-pid=\"1897136601\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136601.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/64/83/bdf2fc04a95c2ab229a44bb06d02d561.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/64/83/bdf2fc04a95c2ab229a44bb06d02d561.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136601\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897696944\">\r\n                                                                                                        在德顺源，砖茶也是必不可少的。从清代开始，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            （当时叫归化）百姓就对这种来自于鄂湘地区的黑茶情有独钟。<br>\r\n对今天的呼市人来说，砖茶与醋、辣椒，还有稍麦馆这个嘈杂的环境，加起来才是稍麦真正的味道。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136598\" data-seq=\"1897136698\" data-pid=\"1897136598\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136598.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/82/98/69e4214f51e9b3ef3494b12a33d89638.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/82/98/69e4214f51e9b3ef3494b12a33d89638.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136598\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897146148\">\r\n                                                                                                        【德顺源（大盛魁店）】<br>\r\n地址：\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市玉泉区大盛魁商业街1号。<br>\r\n推荐：羊肉大葱稍麦、羊肉沙葱稍麦、煎稍麦、砖茶。<br>\r\n人均消费：20元。<br>\r\n———————————————\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1896766275\" data-index=\"6\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">胖子冰煮羊铜涮锅</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897707736\">\r\n                                                                                                        虽然是夏天，可来\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            不吃一顿涮羊肉火锅，总觉得少了点什么。\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            有着全\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"中国\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>\r\n                                                                                                            最好吃的羊肉之一，当地流行的冰煮羊火锅，绝对值得一尝！<br>\r\n所谓“冰煮羊”，顾名思义就是用冰去煮羊肉，这是一种既新派又古老的涮羊肉吃法。说它新派，是相比起传统的羊肉铜涮锅，冰煮羊作为餐饮店真正兴起其实只有大约十年的时间。<br>\r\n说它古老，则是因为冰煮羊这种烹饪手段，可以追溯到公元十三世纪的成吉思汗时代，是一种非常原始的涮羊肉方式——古时冬季人们在草原上取\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/26088.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"淡水\" target=\"_blank\">淡水</a>\r\n                                                                                                            非常困难，因此取冰雪煮羊肉就成了一种很常规的手段。<br>\r\n翔哥去的这家是胖子冰煮羊铜涮锅，除了人气超高的冰煮羊，他家传统铜涮锅的口碑也是不错的。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135416\" data-seq=\"1897135497\" data-pid=\"1897135416\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135416.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/cd/1de0ab27367e4a05cc9f58e629f16939.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/cd/1de0ab27367e4a05cc9f58e629f16939.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/cd/1de0ab27367e4a05cc9f58e629f16939.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135416\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897709185\">\r\n                                                                                                        店里冰煮羊的专用食材是鲜羊肉，有羊肉和羊排可选，我们选的是四子王羔羊肉。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63333.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"四子王旗\" target=\"_blank\">四子王旗</a>\r\n                                                                                                            是\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11572.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"乌兰察布\" target=\"_blank\">乌兰察布</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的羊肉主产区，那里羊肉的品质本身就是极好的——高端的食材往往只需要简单的烹饪方式，因此选择清汤锅底就可以了。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897803339\" data-seq=\"1897803340\" data-pid=\"1897803339\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897803339.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/f9/826b3b78dd7850e683c48afe29a40a7b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/f9/826b3b78dd7850e683c48afe29a40a7b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/f9/826b3b78dd7850e683c48afe29a40a7b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897803339\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897803341\">\r\n                                                                                                        羊肉被切成块放置在冰块上，放入洋葱、大葱等佐料，倒上矿泉水开始煮，不一会儿冰块就在炉子的热力下全部融化，幻化为翻滚的羊汤。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135418\" data-seq=\"1897135499\" data-pid=\"1897135418\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135418.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/79/805004ef711b05458b55a5fb0bdc4002.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/79/805004ef711b05458b55a5fb0bdc4002.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4f/79/805004ef711b05458b55a5fb0bdc4002.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135418\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897711401\">\r\n                                                                                                        煮至沸腾，空气中弥散着羊肉的浓香，此时羊肉就可以食用了。<br>\r\n不少人觉得冰煮羊是一个噱头，事实并非如此，用冰块煮羊肉的确能赋予羊肉更佳的口感——冰水可以减缓羊肉的受热速度，形成一种类似低温慢煮的效果，从而避免蛋白质硬化和水分流失，更大程度地保留羊肉的风味。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135419\" data-seq=\"1897135500\" data-pid=\"1897135419\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135419.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e2/ad/be1c5777af13e914394e70639f1f7a5f.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e2/ad/be1c5777af13e914394e70639f1f7a5f.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/e2/ad/be1c5777af13e914394e70639f1f7a5f.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135419\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897714089\">\r\n                                                                                                        店里的冰煮羊蘸料是在二八酱（芝麻酱与花生酱配比二比八）的基础上调配的，滋味颇有内蒙当地特色。当然，店里也有其它酱料，可以根据自己的口味喜好任意diy。<br>\r\n拿起筷子夹上一块羊肉，在蘸料里蘸一圈放进嘴里，鲜美丰盈的肉香瞬间在口腔中爆发！口感细嫩紧致而有弹性，完全没有膻味，太好吃了！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897714060\" data-seq=\"1897714061\" data-pid=\"1897714060\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897714060.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/80/a916d390fe174ffae15800d1fd608282.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/80/a916d390fe174ffae15800d1fd608282.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/5c/80/a916d390fe174ffae15800d1fd608282.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897714060\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897713372\">\r\n                                                                                                        吃完第一轮冰煮羊后意犹未尽，还可以继续以铜涮锅的方式涮肉。<br>\r\n我们先要了一盘锡盟羔羊后腿肉，锡盟就是\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10704.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"锡林郭勒\" target=\"_blank\">锡林郭勒</a>\r\n                                                                                                            盟，那里拥有非常广阔的草原，著名的苏尼特羊和乌珠穆沁羊都产自锡盟。<br>\r\n这款羊后腿肉虽为冷冻，却是原切而非拼接，红白相间的上好羊肉被刨成薄片，往汤锅里一涮，夹起蘸上点儿蘸料，鲜嫩的羊肉变得更加香润，滋味也是不同凡响！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135421\" data-seq=\"1897135502\" data-pid=\"1897135421\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135421.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/60/649ffc1f8aa1d5c1cb173498739e958e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/60/649ffc1f8aa1d5c1cb173498739e958e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/10/60/649ffc1f8aa1d5c1cb173498739e958e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135421\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897717841\">\r\n                                                                                                        不止是羊肉，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            的牛肉同样名声在外。<br>\r\n我们尝了店里的牧区小牛肉，夹肉开涮一口下去，肉质鲜嫩而有嚼劲，满嘴都是纯正香浓的肉味，就连油脂也是自带香气。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135422\" data-seq=\"1897135503\" data-pid=\"1897135422\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135422.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/62/d3/85ffb0c2aee269cd3adef2181056a9ae.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/62/d3/85ffb0c2aee269cd3adef2181056a9ae.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/62/d3/85ffb0c2aee269cd3adef2181056a9ae.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135422\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897719600\">\r\n                                                                                                        吃涮羊肉时，可以要一瓶雪鹿啤酒。这款啤酒诞生于\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11574.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"包头\" target=\"_blank\">包头</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，虽然现在被燕京收购了，但产地仍然在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，算是当地的啤酒品牌，能喝酒的话不妨尝尝。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897135417\" data-seq=\"1897135498\" data-pid=\"1897135417\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897135417.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8c/b1/fe8a2108a3ed7b9091d46f3ac6b58b62.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8c/b1/fe8a2108a3ed7b9091d46f3ac6b58b62.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897135417\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897146252\">\r\n                                                                                                        【胖子冰煮羊铜锅涮（东影北路店）】<br>\r\n地址：\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64946.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新城\" target=\"_blank\">新城</a>\r\n                                                                                                            区东影北路006号旁。<br>\r\n推荐：清汤锅、四子王羔羊肉、锡盟羔羊后腿肉、牧区小牛肉。<br>\r\n人均消费：70元。<br>\r\n———————————————\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1896766270\" data-index=\"7\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">德乐海蒙餐</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897721901\">\r\n                                                                                                        在呼市美食的浩瀚海洋中，自然少不了蒙餐的身影。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            地理跨度很大，狭义上的蒙餐其实相当于是河套地区\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            族的菜系，传统食材主要有“白食”和“红食”两种。通俗来讲，“白食”即各种奶制品，“红食”就是各种肉，这两大类食材构成了蒙餐的基本盘。<br>\r\n翔哥去的这家德乐海蒙餐，据说是呼市其中一个比较老牌的蒙餐餐馆。话说回来，呼市的蒙餐大多是改良过的，比阴山以北农牧区的纯正蒙餐，更符合大众的口味。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136588\" data-seq=\"1897136688\" data-pid=\"1897136588\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136588.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a7/c5/24093ff267a5b455391d7390c41069de.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a7/c5/24093ff267a5b455391d7390c41069de.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136588\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897853220\">\r\n                                                                                                        在内蒙人的餐桌上，少不了奶制品的身影，当中最常出现的无疑是奶茶。<br>\r\n蒙式奶茶是用砖茶与牛奶煮的，奶香味伴随着淡淡的茶香。对\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            族人来说，奶茶更像是解腻消食的热汤，因此传统的蒙式奶茶会配上些许盐。<br>\r\n喝的时候也可以加一些炒米，这种用糜子炒出来的配料，在浸泡后会变软，淡淡的焦香味能让奶茶的口感变得更丰富。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136594\" data-seq=\"1897136694\" data-pid=\"1897136594\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136594.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c0/47/f21cd9e7a47c79808075b09b21209e01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/c0/47/f21cd9e7a47c79808075b09b21209e01.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136594\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897893543\">\r\n                                                                                                        除了蒙式奶茶，店家自制的酸奶也值得一尝。<br>\r\n相比起外地市面上售卖的酸奶，以传统做法发酵制作的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            酸奶，奶香特别馥郁，质地浓稠得就像布丁，不过味道非常酸！吃的时候根据个人喜好加入白糖或蜜糖，吃上一口余味悠长。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136590\" data-seq=\"1897136690\" data-pid=\"1897136590\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136590.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/86/cb/a75c3dae75bdcb9142e692aec97718f0.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/86/cb/a75c3dae75bdcb9142e692aec97718f0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136590\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897862422\">\r\n                                                                                                        作为蒙餐“红食”的代表，翔哥肯定不会错过这里的烤羊排。<br>\r\n这儿的烤羊排选用的是肋排，表面烤得金黄焦脆滋滋冒油，里面却饱含汁水，恰到好处的油脂包裹着羊肉，啃起来相当细嫩。<br>\r\n烤羊排本身用了盐调味，此外店家还给烤羊排配了三种蘸料：辣椒面、花生碎和甜辣酱。不同风味的蘸料使羊肉的鲜香味得到最大限度的释放，最终在舌尖温柔地化开！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136591\" data-seq=\"1897136691\" data-pid=\"1897136591\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136591.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/80/12/4fa2bf06dbf5b168b133ad026ad9a905.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/80/12/4fa2bf06dbf5b168b133ad026ad9a905.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/80/12/4fa2bf06dbf5b168b133ad026ad9a905.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136591\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897860356\">\r\n                                                                                                        蒙餐的另一道代表菜肴是手把肉，这种肉的做法是把带骨的羊肉按骨节拆开，仅加清水煮熟。类似的白煮做法在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/31808.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西北\" target=\"_blank\">西北</a>\r\n                                                                                                            被称为手抓羊肉，唯独\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            人叫它手把肉——更确切地说是手扒肉，因为传统吃法是用要用手扒着吃。<br>\r\n手把肉煮得很软烂，轻轻一挼就脱骨。羊肉肥瘦相间没有任何膻味，肉质非常鲜嫩！<br>\r\n与烤羊排类似，手把肉也有三种蘸料：韭菜花酱、辣酱和蒜泥醋，翔哥要强推他们家的韭菜花酱，咸鲜的味道不仅解腻，还能调动味蕾，把羊肉的肉香烘托到更高的level！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136592\" data-seq=\"1897136692\" data-pid=\"1897136592\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136592.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4c/dd/6a93e4dc375f5aa20d6d409b40768363.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4c/dd/6a93e4dc375f5aa20d6d409b40768363.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/4c/dd/6a93e4dc375f5aa20d6d409b40768363.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136592\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897891527\">\r\n                                                                                                        事实上，在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            族的传统饮食里，除了“白食”和“红食”，还有“青食”和“棕食（或称紫食）”。其中“青食”指的是蔬菜类食材，例如这道炝拌沙葱。<br>\r\n翔哥在前面介绍稍麦的时候，说过沙葱是一种生长在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/31808.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"西北\" target=\"_blank\">西北</a>\r\n                                                                                                            中、高海拔的野菜，其实沙葱除了拿来做稍麦馅儿，也会被当地人直接当作蔬菜食用，炝拌的做法最能突出它的爽口清新，甚至还能吃出几分清甜。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136589\" data-seq=\"1897136689\" data-pid=\"1897136589\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136589.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/4e/052e0a6fe813da835dda7a4bd37f96c6.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/4e/052e0a6fe813da835dda7a4bd37f96c6.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a0/4e/052e0a6fe813da835dda7a4bd37f96c6.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136589\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897893075\">\r\n                                                                                                        至于蒙餐里所谓的“棕食”，有时也被叫做“紫食”，则泛指碳水类食物。<br>\r\n店里的奶酪饼出品很惊艳，外层烤得很脆，内里奶酪香气浓郁，咬开是满满的拉丝，仿佛让人有一种在吃“蒙式披萨”的感觉，越嚼越香！<br>\r\nps：这个奶酪饼一定要趁热吃，凉了是对奶酪的大不敬！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136593\" data-seq=\"1897136693\" data-pid=\"1897136593\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136593.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/74/37/a3cb06bd1e9ee2cb85b9e6bc4ecd3c55.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/74/37/a3cb06bd1e9ee2cb85b9e6bc4ecd3c55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/74/37/a3cb06bd1e9ee2cb85b9e6bc4ecd3c55.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136593\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897897124\">\r\n                                                                                                        他们家的牛肉馅饼也值得一尝，外表煎得酥脆，里面的肉馅也很硬核，牛肉特有的香气扑面而来。轻轻咬上一口，内里牛肉香气四溢，好吃到根本停不下来！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897136595\" data-seq=\"1897136695\" data-pid=\"1897136595\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897136595.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8d/1d/6717a2b13cffc201f5a9684e70381f86.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8d/1d/6717a2b13cffc201f5a9684e70381f86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/8d/1d/6717a2b13cffc201f5a9684e70381f86.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897136595\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897146204\">\r\n                                                                                                        【德乐海蒙餐】<br>\r\n地址：\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64946.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新城\" target=\"_blank\">新城</a>\r\n                                                                                                            区\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64946.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新城\" target=\"_blank\">新城</a>\r\n                                                                                                            东街75号。<br>\r\n推荐：奶茶、酸奶、\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            烤羊排、草原手把肉、炝拌沙葱、奶酪饼、牛肉馅饼。<br>\r\n人均消费：80元。<br>\r\n———————————————\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1896766313\" data-index=\"8\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">苏尼特骨头馆</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897721936\">\r\n                                                                                                        这家苏尼特骨头馆，是翔哥在离开呼市前的最后一顿正餐。<br>\r\n\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            羊肉的美味难以让人释怀，尽管已经在呼市吃过了冰煮羊、手把羊肉和烤羊排，却还是有些意犹未尽，于是翔哥又把目光放在了羊骨头汤上。<br>\r\n当地人说的羊骨头汤，实际上相当于炖羊蝎子，而这家店最大的卖点是他家羊肉的产地——\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10704.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"锡林郭勒\" target=\"_blank\">锡林郭勒</a>\r\n                                                                                                            盟\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63391.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"苏尼特右旗\" target=\"_blank\">苏尼特右旗</a>\r\n                                                                                                            。当地产的苏尼特羊，品质在整个\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12720.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"内蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            都算得上是天花板！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137312\" data-seq=\"1897137373\" data-pid=\"1897137312\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137312.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/56/4e/7fa7dc4d1a7f8a84db31530ed6f58ee7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/56/4e/7fa7dc4d1a7f8a84db31530ed6f58ee7.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/56/4e/7fa7dc4d1a7f8a84db31530ed6f58ee7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137312\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897723549\">\r\n                                                                                                        店里的招牌自然是羊骨头汤，因为食材的品质有保证，所以店里的羊骨头汤做法就是清炖，调料除了大葱就只有盐，大道至简，却最能突出羊肉本身的鲜香。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897802741\" data-seq=\"1897802742\" data-pid=\"1897802741\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897802741.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/2a/00f252fa34226835b726893a967466e4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/2a/00f252fa34226835b726893a967466e4.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/eb/2a/00f252fa34226835b726893a967466e4.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897802741\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897802743\">\r\n                                                                                                        汤里的羊骨头，用的是俗称“羊蝎子”的羊脊骨，这个部位有筋也有肉，还能嗦到白色软糯的骨髓，味道鲜而不膻，属于越嚼越香的选手。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137314\" data-seq=\"1897137375\" data-pid=\"1897137314\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137314.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/70/74/cd2425ea2cd2a9f64abcd653c687aff0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/70/74/cd2425ea2cd2a9f64abcd653c687aff0.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/70/74/cd2425ea2cd2a9f64abcd653c687aff0.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137314\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897776882\">\r\n                                                                                                        这里羊骨头汤之所以好吃，关键还在于他家自制的灵魂蘸料：辣酱和韭菜花酱。<br>\r\n特别是韭菜花酱，比一般外面的韭菜花酱更有颗粒感，与其说是酱，不如说是韭菜花末。吃羊骨头时蘸上一点儿，层次感立刻就出来了，微微的咸与辛香让人吃过一次就忘不了！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897776861\" data-seq=\"1897776862\" data-pid=\"1897776861\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897776861.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/fc/d4/6027bd6d41d52e21197d1803471450f1.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/fc/d4/6027bd6d41d52e21197d1803471450f1.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897776861\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897749294\">\r\n                                                                                                        他们家除了羊骨头汤，还卖各种牛羊肉或内脏。老板娘热情地向翔哥介绍他们家的食材，能选择的部位很多，包括羊排、牛排、牛蹄筋、羊肚，还有羊肉肠和羊血肠，最后干脆每样都抓一点，弄了个牛羊拼盘。<br>\r\n这些食材都是事先煮熟的，称好后，店员会拿去在后厨切好，端上桌就能直接食用。牛羊排肉香十足，牛蹄筋吃起来有微妙的弹性，羊肚则是脆弹中带一点柔软，还有羊肉肠和羊血肠的口感也很独特。<br>\r\nps：假如觉得有些凉了，也可以放进羊骨头汤里汆烫热一下，大快朵颐起来也是绝了！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137315\" data-seq=\"1897137376\" data-pid=\"1897137315\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137315.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"_j_lazyload\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/15/12/a96c82db0e737166b40438b8d3654b7b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/15/12/a96c82db0e737166b40438b8d3654b7b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137315\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897799201\">\r\n                                                                                                        这家店的包子，在呼市当地也算是小有名气。包子馅儿有羊肉和羊血两种，由于翔哥一个人食量实在有限，所以只尝了一个羊血包子（毕竟翔哥以前从未吃过羊血包子）。<br>\r\n这儿的羊血包子个头非常大，用羊血肠、羊肉和沙葱做馅儿，三样食材组成了巧妙的搭配——羊血肠和羊肉的香气油润不腻，沙葱完美地去除了羊血的腥膻味，同时淡淡的辛香赋予了包子更浓重的地域风味，咬上第一口，就让翔哥大有相见恨晚之感！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137316\" data-seq=\"1897137377\" data-pid=\"1897137316\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137316.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ed/b2/ad0e4b8ab09f02cd826c99e278659321.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ed/b2/ad0e4b8ab09f02cd826c99e278659321.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ed/b2/ad0e4b8ab09f02cd826c99e278659321.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137316\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897146225\">\r\n                                                                                                        【苏尼特骨头馆】<br>\r\n地址：\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64946.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"新城\" target=\"_blank\">新城</a>\r\n                                                                                                            区\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63612.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"兴安\" target=\"_blank\">兴安</a>\r\n                                                                                                            北路11号。<br>\r\n推荐：羊脊骨汤、牛羊拼盘、羊血包子。<br>\r\n人均消费：90元。<br>\r\n———————————————\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1897139626\" data-index=\"9\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">乌珠穆沁奶茶馆</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897930719\">\r\n                                                                                                        由于牧区的特殊性，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            族一日餐食的重点在于早餐，牧民们要在早餐上摄取足够的能量去完成一日的劳作。<br>\r\n接下来要说的这家乌珠穆沁奶茶馆，主打一个硬核早餐，他们家的所有食材，据说都来自\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10704.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"锡林郭勒\" target=\"_blank\">锡林郭勒</a>\r\n                                                                                                            盟的乌珠穆沁草原。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137317\" data-seq=\"1897137378\" data-pid=\"1897137317\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137317.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1b/a8/f977aea1a63a27de39eefb080dba79cc.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1b/a8/f977aea1a63a27de39eefb080dba79cc.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/1b/a8/f977aea1a63a27de39eefb080dba79cc.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137317\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897853268\">\r\n                                                                                                        传统的\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"蒙古\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>\r\n                                                                                                            族早餐，通常会有奶茶存在，这是因为传统奶茶咸酥的口感，很容易能让身体从困倦中清醒。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137319\" data-seq=\"1897137380\" data-pid=\"1897137319\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137319.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/4a/a26d6ea5bcb78edd9678cd43396e828e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/4a/a26d6ea5bcb78edd9678cd43396e828e.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/51/4a/a26d6ea5bcb78edd9678cd43396e828e.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137319\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897854107\">\r\n                                                                                                        蒙式奶茶有一样经典搭配叫奶皮子，这种极具地域色彩的食物是牛奶中的精华，笼统来说其实就是煮牛奶时表面凝结的那层膜——如果煮的时间足够长，同时不断用勺子扬动奶液，牛奶表面会形成一层厚厚蜂窝状膜，晾干脱水之后就是奶皮子。<br>\r\n奶皮子的地道吃法，是把它泡进奶茶里，捞起来吃上一口，一股浓烈的奶香在嘴里瞬间迸发出来，好吃到爆炸！\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137318\" data-seq=\"1897137379\" data-pid=\"1897137318\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137318.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/89/c76ca7103d609c567c063e29f05794d7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/89/c76ca7103d609c567c063e29f05794d7.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/a8/89/c76ca7103d609c567c063e29f05794d7.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137318\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897933300\">\r\n                                                                                                        当地人喝奶茶，还会配上羊肉沙葱包。包子皮薄馅大，羊肉与沙葱是一对很经典的CP，一口咬开，热气腾腾的羊肉被沙葱香气萦绕，很好吃。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137320\" data-seq=\"1897137381\" data-pid=\"1897137320\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137320.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 454px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d2/f2/979b6ef1ba61813f16346477c2b15f34.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d2/f2/979b6ef1ba61813f16346477c2b15f34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d2/f2/979b6ef1ba61813f16346477c2b15f34.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137320\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897854884\">\r\n                                                                                                        他们家的酱牛肉倒是一绝，部位是腱子肉，可以看见丝丝缕缕的筋络和肌肉纤维。做酱牛肉需要用到许多种调料，味道浓郁得很。嚼上一口，肉香在嘴里如泉水般涌动，感觉太棒了！<br>\r\n最后说一个小tips，酱牛肉是一道凉菜，如果觉得牛肉太冷，也可以在热奶茶里泡一泡再吃，口感更好。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1897137321\" data-seq=\"1897137382\" data-pid=\"1897137321\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11415/scenery_24514256/1897137321.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1018px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f4/20/4bb43f176df84f46bab6c9da3b92ef7b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f4/20/4bb43f176df84f46bab6c9da3b92ef7b.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/f4/20/4bb43f176df84f46bab6c9da3b92ef7b.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1897137321\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1897146197\">\r\n                                                                                                        【乌珠穆沁奶茶馆（满都\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16813.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"海西\" target=\"_blank\">海西</a>\r\n                                                                                                            巷店）】<br>\r\n地址：\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11415.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"呼和浩特\" target=\"_blank\">呼和浩特</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市赛罕区满都\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16813.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"海西\" target=\"_blank\">海西</a>\r\n                                                                                                            巷。<br>\r\n推荐：奶茶、奶皮子、羊肉沙葱包、酱牛肉。<br>\r\n人均消费：40元。<br>\r\n———————————————\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n           \r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\r\n                                    </div>",
