    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "The cozy provincial capital that met because of the concert - weekend [Fuzhou]",
      "descr": "I have been to Pingtan twice, but I have never stopped in downtown Fuzhou. Because I grabbed Jay Chou's concert tickets, I specially arranged a trip to Fuzhou.",
      "cover": "http://localhost:9090/files/download/22.jpeg",
      "content": "<div class=\"vc_article\">\r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            <div class=\"va_con _j_master_content\" data-cs-t=\"ginfo_kw_hotel\">\r\n    <div class=\"block-loading loading_backward\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"_j_content_box\">\r\n\t        <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898131276\">\r\n                                                                                                        去过两次\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10702.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"平潭\" target=\"_blank\">平潭</a>\r\n                                                                                                            ，却从未在\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11498.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"福州\" target=\"_blank\">福州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            市区停留过。因为抢到了周杰伦演唱会门票所以特意安排了一趟\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11498.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"福州\" target=\"_blank\">福州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            行。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129652\" data-seq=\"1898131175\" data-pid=\"1898129652\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"15420\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129652.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/46/1c/b427bfb571e3f5c9d3283f064ba78b90.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/46/1c/b427bfb571e3f5c9d3283f064ba78b90.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/46/1c/b427bfb571e3f5c9d3283f064ba78b90.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129652\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/15420.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15420\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>鼓山\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898131174\" data-seq=\"1898131176\" data-pid=\"1898131174\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"15420\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898131174.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/98/4b3b80d90fc035179a1bc2f0ea38cdc8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/98/4b3b80d90fc035179a1bc2f0ea38cdc8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d0/98/4b3b80d90fc035179a1bc2f0ea38cdc8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898131174\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/15420.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15420\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_n