502.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15502\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州西湖公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898677909\">\r\n                                                                                                        带着水汽的风掠过，带走一切喧嚣杂音，看着岸边不断变换，创意园区，老居民区，带雕塑的广场，我们是坐在最佳观赏位的城市观察者，\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11498.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"福州\" target=\"_blank\">福州</a>\r\n                                                                                                            最隐秘的生活气息尽收眼底。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129677\" data-seq=\"1898129775\" data-pid=\"1898129677\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"15502\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129677.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7e/fa/b7dec05b340ef88c1ef3814f25702ef8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7e/fa/b7dec05b340ef88c1ef3814f25702ef8.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/7e/fa/b7dec05b340ef88c1ef3814f25702ef8.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129677\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/15502.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15502\" target=\"_blank\