f/17/da86bb66d51046d6a23f65def250ef17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/ef/17/da86bb66d51046d6a23f65def250ef17.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129679\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/15502.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15502\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州西湖公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129680\" data-seq=\"1898129778\" data-pid=\"1898129680\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"15502\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129680.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b9/d1/cdece3f49fceb57d779f8cef302960e5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b9/d1/cdece3f49fceb57d779f8cef302960e5.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/b9/d1/cdece3f49fceb57d779f8cef302960e5.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129680\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/15502.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15502\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州西湖公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129681\" data-seq=\"1898129779\" data-pid=\"1898129681\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"15502\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129681.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d6/07/f8fb79515051f563b49526b16b83ddd3.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d6/07/f8fb79515051f563b49526b16b83ddd3.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/d6/07/f8fb79515051f563b49526b16b83ddd3.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129681\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/15502.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15502\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州西湖公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898678089\">\r\n                                                                                                        同样有趣的是进入西湖前的“水上电梯”，体验水涨船高。<br>\r\n由于西湖的水位会比白马湖的高，船先开进第一道船闸，第一道船闸升起，再打开第二道船闸，水位抬升，船也同西湖水位平齐，就可以驶入西湖了。\r\n                                                                                                        <a href=\"/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10705.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"三峡\" target=\"_blank\">三峡</a>\r\n                                                                                                            大坝也使用了相同的船闸原理。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129682\" data-seq=\"1898129780\" data-pid=\"1898129682\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"15502\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129682.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/02/fd/fc6cebaceaff18062687196b3e628f36.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/02/fd/fc6cebaceaff18062687196b3e628f36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/02/fd/fc6cebaceaff18062687196b3e628f36.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129682\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/15502.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"15502\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福州西湖公园\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898991154\">\r\n                                                                                                        船驶进西湖，湖面豁然开朗。远远看着湖边的热闹，和刚才的水上秘境是完全不同的氛围了。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div data-seq=\"1898991194\" data-index=\"11\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"t9\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\">-福道</span></h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1898991217\">\r\n                                                                                                        门票：无门票 游玩时间：2-3h<br>\r\n城市森林步道环线总长19km，采用的钢架镂空设计，可以很好地隐于森林中。<br>\r\n网红路线是5号口进，3号口出。5号口适合看日落，3号口适合看蓝调夜幕下的灯光。\r\n                                                                                </p>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129683\" data-seq=\"1898129781\" data-pid=\"1898129683\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"71753504\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129683.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3e/19/19d18f52633aa640873e41cf7d211c35.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3e/19/19d18f52633aa640873e41cf7d211c35.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/3e/19/19d18f52633aa640873e41cf7d211c35.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"1898129683\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </a>\r\n                                        <span class=\"pic_tag\">\r\n                <a href=\"/poi/71753504.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"71753504\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\">\r\n                    <i class=\"house\"></i>福道\r\n                </a>\r\n            </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n            <div id=\"_j_photo_1898129684\" data-seq=\"1898129782\" data-pid=\"1898129684\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"width:680px\" data-poiid=\"71753504\">\r\n        <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: block\" href=\"/photo/11498/scenery_24515641/1898129684.html\">\r\n            <img class=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\" src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/66/f0/37ba05491159658c2b2f39748b29fdba.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://note.mafengwo.net/img/66/f0/37ba05491159658c2b2f39748b29fdba.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1280%2Fq%2F50%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F50\" data-rt-src=\"https://not